\id EXO Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93
\h EKESETASE
\toc1 EKESETASE
\toc2 Ekesetase
\toc3 Ek
\mt1 EKESETASE
\imt1 Isipi Yaki Nyuo Peyaminyi Pii Doko
\ip Yaki nyuo peyaminyi doko Ekesetase lenge. Isaraele wambu dupwame yuu Isipi dokona kendemande wambu ingyuo karo Isipi doko yaki nyuo peyaminyi dokona lao Isaraele wambunya arome pii mupwa pyasi palamo. Arome pii dake buku Ekesetase lenge dokona palamo dokona kingi Ekesetase dake yaka lenge dokopa arome pii dakeme dokona lao suu pingi. Buku Ekesetase dake mendaki sipyamopape arome pii liti rema ingyuo pyasi palamo.
\io1 \bk 1. Rombo 1-18 \bk*Ipuru wambu dupwa kendemande yulu piyaminyi doko moko manda rao nyiyamo pao yuu kyau Sainai lenge dokona peyaminyi pii dolapo pyasi palamo.
\io1 \bk 2. Rombo 19-24 \bk*Anatupa Ipuru wambu dupwa pipya yuu kyau Sainai dokona kana minyuo lalu lao leyami arome pii doko palamo. Anatumi Ipuru wambu dupwa reke lao mawa pii dupwa maiya. Maiyamo dusipa Anatu lakandenge mawa pii dusipa pipya wambu yalya kando role pyao randa nyii nao karenge mawa pii dusipa pyasi palamo.
\io1 \bk 3. Rombo 25-40 \bk*Isaraele wambu dupwa Anatu lakandenge anda pyuo bange taepope bange misi anda singi dupwa retarami lao mawa pii dusipa palamo. Purisi dupwana yulu wakale wakale dupwana mawa pii dupwa pipya misi anda lakandenge yulu pii dupwa pyasi palamoko.
\ip Anatumi Isaraele wambu dupwa anjisi kareyaminyipa moko nyiya. Moko nyiyamo dokopa wambu dupwa yuku peyami. Peyaminyi dokopa Anatumi wambu dupwa enenge inginyi pyambuya.
\ip Buku dakena akali Mosese lenge baa mupwa ingilyamo. Anatumi baa Isaraele wambu yuu Isipi karo lanyuo paeyara lao rombo palyiya.
\ip Buku Ekesetase lenge dakena mawa pii akalisa rombo 20 dokona palyapyamo dokona lao wambu yuu muu dupwana kareyami dupwame siyamilyamo.
\ip Anatunya porai renge dokome Mosese keta yulu pipala kiŋi Peraona suu pingi alowa piyamopa baame Ipuru wambu dupwa neta pena leya. Anatunya porai renge dokomeko Ipuru wambu dupwa kyawa minyiyamopa yuu Sainai dokona pena peyami.
\c 1
\s1 Isipi Wambu Dupwame Isaraele Wambu Dupwa Randa Andake Maiyami
\p 
\v 1 Jekope yuu Isipi banya wane dupwa pipya peyami. Nakama nakamana enda wanepe dupwa role pyao peyami. Jekopena wanena kingi dupwa dakena palamo.
\v 2 Urupene Simione Lipae Juta
\v 3 Isaka Sepyulane Benjamene
\v 4 Dane Napatalai Gate dee Asamoo peyami.
\v 5 Jekopena wane mandeyamo dupwa para piyamo dupwa peparae nyuo pyaso akalisa yanda ipingi nyepo (70) ingiyamopa Isipi pao kareyami. Dokopa Josepe baa yuu Isipi wambo papala kareya.
\v 6 Josepemoo yangonge dusipape wambu kapa kapa kareyaminyi dupwa peparaepe Isipi karo kumuyami.
\v 7 Dopa piyamopape Isaraele wambu nakamana para piyamo dupwana wane wanakepe mandeyami doko ama malu mee ingyapala porai ingyuo karo yuu doko simbuya.
\p 
\v 8 Dopa pyuo peyamo yuu gii dokopa kiŋi enenge mende Josepe soo gisa nangendeme yuu Isipi dokona rapu piya.
\v 9 Kiŋi dokome Isipi range wambu dupwa lamaiyuo dopa leya. Kandalapape. Isaraele wambu dupwa ama malu mee ingyuo porailyaminyi.
\v 10 Dokona yanda mende sipuro pira ramo dokopa namwana nyisu petenge doko keta nakamba ree maipala namwa pyapala nakamba pasaramiŋi dokona namwame Isaraele wambu dupwa ama kandokondali pyuo rapu pirama. Wambu wai malu mee kisilyamo doko isa pena lao rapu pimanale, lamaiya.
\v 11 Dokopa Isipi akali lapo Isaraele wambu yulu pinya lao rapu piyami dupwame randa wakasa maiyuo yulu andake pinya lao nyuo maiyami. Dopa piyaminyipa Isaraele wambu dupwame Peraona taone andake lamana nenge retenge Pitomo Oramese lenge dolapo pyakamiyami.
\v 12 Isipi wambu dupwame Isaraele wambu dupwa kumuo ree nao otapyali lapala yulu andake maiyaminyipape doko kaepala Isaraele wambu ama malu ando yuu dupwa minyarambu nyinya piya. Dokona lao Isipi wambu dupwame Isaraele wambu kando pakame kumuyami.
\v 13 Pakame kumapala ama randa andake maiyuo karapusi yulu andake maiyami.
\v 14 Isaraele range wambu dupwa randa maiyuo mona kendanyi pyambuo ee yulupi anda pingipi poraiyuo pinya leyami. Dopa pyuo karo nakamame Isaraele wambu dupwa kando sakame kuma nao mee randa maiyuoko pyuo kareyami.
\p 
\v 15 Enakana Isipi range kiŋi dokome enda Sipira Puwapa lenge Ipuru enda dupwa wane mandelyaminyi dokopa nyiso mandenge enda dolapo lamaiyuo leya.
\v 16 Nakamba Ipuru enda dupwa wane mandena lao nyiso parambinyi dokopa wane ane ramo doko pyao kumako wanake ramo doko andena kaeyo pipwape, lamaiya.
\v 17 Dopa lamaiyamopape enda dolapome Anatu dokona lao poraiyuo suu pyao pakapala kiŋimi pinya leyamuli pyuo pii napala Ipuru wane dupwa ando karena kaeyambi.
\v 18 Dokopa kiŋi dokome dopa piyambinyi kandapala Sipira Puwapa epena lapala piso soo, Akipamo doo lapu doko pii napala wane dupwa mee ando pena kaeyambisi? leya.
\p 
\v 19 Dokopa enda dolapome isingi leyambi. Isaraele enda dupwa Isipi enda dopalende daa. Ipuru enda dupwa awa pyuo waiya lao wane manjo otelyaminyipa nambwa enakana papapu pingi, leyambi.
\v 20 Enda dolapo Anatu baa poraiyuo suu pyao pakayambi dokona baame nakamba keta keyange pyuo rangena wane wai kiso maiya.
\v 21 Maiyamopa Isaraele wambu dupwa konda pyuo manjoko pao porai ingyuo ando kareyami.
\v 22 Dokopa kiŋi Perao dokome mawa pii dake poraiyuo lamaiyuo Ipuru wane nyaŋa manjiraminyi dupwa nyuo ipwa Naelena pyao nembo wanake dupwa andena kaeyo pinya leya.
\c 2
\s1 Mosese Manjipala Yalu Piyami
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa akali Lipaena rara dokona mendeme enda rara mendaki dokonako nyiya.
\v 2 Nyiyamopa enda baa wane paleyamopa wane ane mende manjo nyiya. Manjo nyepala enda dokome wane doko ama keyange wakasa ingiyamosa kandapala kana rema yalu pyuo reteya.
\v 3 Enakana wane doko kapa pyuo yalu pira ingya nayamosa pisiki minyasi mende ipwa yalyo pii nana lapala mamba pyake rengendeme kiso rambu lao mondo leya. Dopa pipala pisiki minyasi dokona Mosese retapala ipwa pona nemba nemba dokona wae wae ando londo kareya dokona koko yalu pyuo reteya.
\v 4 Dokopa Mosesena pemalenge dokome yuu nanesale karo apa pyakalyape lao rapu pyuo kando kareya.
\p 
\v 5 Dokopa kiŋi Peraona wanenge doko ipwa dokona wate pela epeyamo dokopa banya kendemande enda dupwa opetae ipwa nemba nemba dokona epeyami. Dokopa Peraona wanenge dokome pisiki minyasi doko kandapala banya kendemande wanake mendeme nyela pena leya.
\v 6 Dokopa Peraona wanenge dokome nyepala lumbuo kandeyamo dokopa wane nyaŋa doko ee leya. Ee leyamo doko kandapala kondome kumuya. Dokopa Peraona wanenge dokome lao, Wane doko Ipuru wane dupwana mendelamo, leya.
\p 
\v 7 Dokopa Mosesena pemalenge doko epapala piso soo leya. Nambame Isaraele enda mende wane doko rapu pyakana lao kotala paowape? leya.
\p 
\v 8 Dokopa Peraona wanenge dokome lamaiyuo, Kapa mendali kotakala pena leya. Dokopa wanake dokome papala Mosesena endangi angi range doko nyepala lanyuo epeya.
\v 9 Peraona wanenge dokome Mosesena endangi doko lamaiyuo, Wane doko nyepala anju maiyuo rapu pyakape. Nambame emba ropo pyaro, leya.
\v 10 Mosesena endangi dokome rapu pyuo peteyamopa wane doko ando oteya dokopa wane doko minyuo pao Peraona wanenge maiya. Dokopa Mosese Peraona wanengena ikinyingi ingiya. Peraona wanenge dokome wane doko ipwana siyamo nyiyuŋu lapala wane kingi Mosese leto, leya. (Kingi Mosese lenge doko ipwana silyamo nyingi dopale lenge.)
\s1 Mosese Yuu Mitiane Pyakao Peya
\p 
\v 11 Yuu mendepa Mosese ando kaepala kareyamo dokopa baa banya Isaraele wambu dupwa apa pyuo yulu andake nyuo maiyaminyi pyuo karamipi lao kandala peya. Peyamo dokopa Isipi akali mendeme Mosese banya wambu rangende pyao kumakayamo kandama peya.
\v 12 Dokopa Mosese kandalya kandana piyamo mendale pana nayaminyi kandapala Isipi akali doko pyao kumakapala ipwa kee dokona yalu piya.
\v 13 Yangama deeko peyamo dokopa Isaraele akali lama pyakando pyuo paleyambinyi kandeya. Dokopa Moseseme akali angi koo piyamo doko lamaiyuo, Akipamo embame Ipuru akali yango doko pilisi? leya.
\p 
\v 14 Dokopa akali dokome isingi lao, Apimi emba kote singi akali wasapala namwa rapu pyuo kara lapyase? Embame Isipi akali pyao kumakapi doko suu pyao namba pyao kumakapuli lao letese? leya. Dopa leyamo dokopa Mosese pakaya. Namba doo pipu kandapi doko wambu dupwa similyamo.
\v 15 Dopa piyamo leyaminyi doko kiŋi Perao sepala Mosese pyao kumakalena piya. Dokopa Mosese yuu Isipi doko yaki nyepala yuu Mitiane dokona karala peya. Mosese baa pao yuu Mitiane kando nyepala kareya. Karo dokopa yuu mendepa yuwale kyasisi dokona ipwa guu lao pete silyamopa kamuo nenge dokona papala isa peteya.
\v 16 Dokopa purisi akali mende kingi Jetero lenge yuu Mitiane doko rangendeme wanake yanda ipingi nyepo mandenge.
\p Wanake dusipa peparae rakangena mena sipisipi memepe dupwa ipwa maiyalana kamwala epeyami.
\v 17 Epeyaminyi dokopa mena sipisipi isingi akali lapome Jeterona wanenge dupwa ralinyi nembeyami. Dopa piyaminyipa Moseseme nakama nyiso mena dupwa ipwa kamuo maiyuo pyakamiya.
\v 18 Dopa pyakamiyamopa wanake dusipa rakange kareyamo dokona waiya lao peyami. Dokopa rakangeme piso soo, Akipamo nakamba epapu waiya lao kapa kyuo epelyamisi? leya.
\p 
\v 19 Dokopa wanake dusipame isingi lao, Mena sipisipi isingi akali dupwame namwa randa jiminyipa akali Isipi rangendeme namwa nyiso mena dupwa ipwa kamuo maiyuoko pipyamosa epelyamano, leyami.
\p 
\v 20 Rakangeme wanenge dupwa piso soo, Akali doko anja karase? Akipamo dokona karena lapala epaminyi? leya. Papala namwa pipya role pyao nenge nala epena lena leya.
\p 
\v 21 Dokopa Mosese baa doo palyuo karo pipuli lao suu pyalu pyao piya. Dopa piyasa Jetero banya wanenge Sipora doko Mosesena etenge inginya lao maiya.
\v 22 Mosese nyepala paleyambinyipa enda dokome wane ane mende mandeya. Mandeyamo dokopa Moseseme namba akali wakale doko yuu wakale dakena karalyano lapala wane kingi Gasome leya. (Kingi Gasome lenge doko yuu wakale range lenge dopale.)
\p 
\v 23 Ee kana malu epo peyamopa Isipi range kiŋi doko kumuya. Dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwa ee lao nakama karapusi yulu pyuo karo makapala mendeme nyisapyali lao ee lao kareyami. Dokopa Anatumi Isaraele wambu ee lao kareyami doko siya.
\v 24 Ee lao kareyami doko sepala Anatumi kana minyuo nyisaroŋo lao Aporakamemoo Aisakemoo Jekopemoo keta lalu lao leyamo doko suu piya.
\v 25 Anatumi Isaraele wambu dupwa karapusi yulu pyuo peteyami doko kandapala baame nakamana lao suu pyaro kareya.
\c 3
\s1 Anatumi Mosese Kee Leya
\p 
\v 1 Mosese banya imwange Jetero yuu Mitiane range purisi akali dokona mena sipisipipi memepe dupwa rapu pyakamyuo kareya. Yuu mendepa baa dopa pyuo karo Mosese mena dupwa lanyuo yuu muiyane dokona pao Anatunya yuu kyau kingi Sainai lenge dokona epeya.
\v 2 Dokopa Kamongona aŋala mende isare uliyapu ingyuo isako ambu pyaro kareyamo dokona rao Mosese keta pano epeya. Mosese isare uliyapu nyuo isako dokona rao karo isako angi doko rao ota nayamo kandeya.
\v 3 Kandapala dopa lao suu pyao, Akipamo isako doko rao ota nalyamo? Angi kanda nangende pilyamoŋo kandala paro lao suu piya.
\p 
\v 4 Kamongo Mosese repeta epeyamo doko kandapala Anatumi isare rao kareyamo isako palu sukusa dokona karo kyakale lao, Mosese, Mosese, leya. Dokopa Moseseme isingi lao, Namba dae karo, leya.
\p 
\v 5 Anatumi Mosese lamaiyuo, Kamame repeta epa napipi. Yuu doo karene doko poo pyasiŋi dokona embena kimbu suu doko kolo nyisa nyepe, leya.
\v 6 Namba embena rakane dusipana Anatuŋu, leya. Leyamo dokonako lao, Aporakamena Anatu Aisakena Anatu Jekopena Anatu dokoŋo leya. Dokopa Mosese Anatu kandalana pakapala banya lenge kambu doko nee piya.
\p 
\v 7 Dokopa Kamongome lao, Nambame nambana wambu dupwa Isipi wambu dupwame randa maiyuo pyuo karaminyi doko kandelyo. Dee karapusi yulu rapu pingi akali dupwame kopetame isilyaminyi dokona kiiramo nyuo pumwali lao ee lao karaminyi doko namba silyu. Randa nami dupwa namba soo gisilyu, leya.
\v 8 Nambame Isipi range dupwana kiiramo nyisala epelyo. Kiiramo nyepala yuu Isipi yaki nyuo yuu ama keyange andake mendena lanyuo paro. Yuu doko keyange amenge pingi. Dakepa akali rara Kenane rangepe Iti rangepe Amo rangepe Perasi rangepe Ipi rangepe dee Jepusi rangepe dupwa yuu dokona palaminyi, leya.
\v 9 Isipi wambumi ama kopetame randa maiyuo karaminyi dokona Isaraele wambu dupwa ee lao karaminyi doko kandelyo.
\v 10 Epapu emba puu laronopa kiŋi Perao petamo dokona papala nambana Isaraele wambu dupwa lanyako yuu Isipi doko yaki nyuo parami, leya.
\p 
\v 11 Dokopa Moseseme Anatu lamaiyuo, Namba apyakalendeme Perao petamo dokona papala Isaraele wambu dupwa kiiramo nyuo Isipi yaki nyerose? leya.
\p 
\v 12 Anatumi isingi lamaiyuo, Nambame emba pipya role pyao kararo. Wambu dupwa lanyuo Isipi yaki nyuo epare dokopa yuu kyau dakena namba kingi lao pisirami. Dopa pirinyi dokome nambame emba puu lapu lao lasaka pirasa pira, lamaiya.
\p 
\v 13 Lamaiyamopa Moseseme Anatu isingi lamaiyuo, Namba Isaraele wambu petaminyi dokona papala nakama lamaiyuo, Anatu nakambana rakane kauwanepe loma soo piyami dokome namba nakama karaminyi dokona puu lapyamo epelyo laro dokopa nakamame namba piso soo, Banya kingi doko apisi? larami. Dokopa nambame nakama kando isingi apa larose? leya. \fig Namba puu lapyamo epano lare. Dake nambana kingi sulu soo sera.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="3:14-15"\fig*
\p 
\v 14 Dokopa Anatumi Mosese lamaiyuo, Namba Doko Nambako. Pii dake embame Isaraele wambu dupwa lamairi. Namba Doko Nambako laypamo dokome namba nakama keta puu lao peyapyamo epano lare.
\v 15 Lapala Isaraele wambu dupwa lamaiyuo lao, Namba Kamongo doko nakamana rakane kauwanepena Anatu Aporakamemoo Aisake Jekope dusipana Anatuko dokome namba puu lapyamo epano lare. Dake nambana kingi sulu soo sera. Dokoko wambu ene manjiraminyi dupwame namba kando larami, leya.
\v 16 Dokopa Anatumi Mosese lamaiyuo, Emba papala Isaraele akali mupwa dupwa nyuo elyambu pipala nakama dopa lamairi. Namba Kamongo doko nakamana rakane kauwanepena Anatu Aporakamemoo Aisake Jekopemoo dusipana Anatuko doko namba keta epo paneya. Panapala nakama langyala pupwa lapyamo epano. Anatu baame nakama Isipi range dupwame doo pyuo karaminyi doko kando karo lapya lare, leya.
\v 17 Nambame suu pilyu doko nakama Isipi wambu dupwame kopetame rapu pyuo karaminyi dokona yuu doko yaki nyuo yuu mende ama keyange amenge pingi dokona lanyuo paro. Yuu dokona Kenane rangepe Iti rangepe Amo rangepe Perasi rangepe Ipi rangepe Jepusi rangepe palaminyi dokona lanyuo paro lapyaŋa lare, leya.
\p 
\v 18 Larenepa nambana wambu dupwame emba lare doko serami, leya. Dokopa Isipi range kiŋi petamo dokona Isaraele akali mupwa dupwa pipya epapala dopa lare. Isaraele wambu dupwana Kamongo Anatu namwa keta epo pii langiya. Dokona lao namwa yuu muiyane dokona yuu gii rema pao mena pyao kiso namwana Kamongo Anatu doko maiyala pupwa lena larami, leya.
\v 19 Yuu range kiŋi dokome nakama mee pupwa laa nara. Mendeme baa kando poraiyuo suu lao lara ramo doko kapa pupwa lara lao namba soo gisilyu.
\v 20 Dokopa nambana porai dokome yulu yamarangunyi pyambungi lapo Isipi wambu randa mairu. Enakana dokopa kiŋi dokome nakama pupwa lapala kaeyara, leya.
\p 
\v 21 Nambame Isipi range wambu dupwame nakamana kingi rape rape lena pirunupa nakama puu pao paraminyi dokopa mee kingipa paa narami.
\v 22 Isaraele enda mendaki mendaki lao dupwame nakamana anda parali maki palenge Isipi wambu dupwape dee Isipi enda yango nakama role pyao palenge dupwape piso soo kana kulingipi kana golope komaupi jinya larami. Isaraele wambu dupwame Isipi wambunya bange nyulu nyuo nyepala nakamana wane wanakepe keta sinyi palyakamirami. Dopa pyuo Isipi wambu dupwa kokwa sinyi nembaramisa pira, leya.
\c 4
\s1 Anatumi Mosese Yulu Wambu Kanda Nange Dupwa Porainya Renge // Andake Maiya
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa Moseseme isingi lao, Dopa pirunupape Isaraele wambu dupwame Kamongo doko emba keta maro laa nalyamo doko lapala kinyi lao suu pyaa nao nambana pii wangu lakao see naraminyi dokopa apa pirusi? leya.
\p 
\v 2 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese kando piso soo, Minyaro karene doko akipi? leya. Moseseme isingi lao, Pangali dokoŋo, lamaiya.
\p 
\v 3 Dokopa Kamongome lao, Yuu dokona yaki nyuo kanda, leya. Moseseme yuunya yaki nyuo kandeyamo dokopa kau ingiyamosa baa pakao ralo peya.
\v 4 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese kando lao, Kingi pyasinju lapala konali dokona minyarapala nyii, leya. Leyamopa Moseseme kingi pyasinju lapala konali dokona rambuki nyepala banya kingi dokona soo dokopa dee pangali ingiya.
\v 5 Dokona lao wambu dupwame nakamana rakange kyawa dupwana Anatu Aporakame Aisake Jekopemoo dusipana Anatuko dokome emba keta epo lapyalyamo lao serami, leya.
\p 
\v 6 Lapala Kamongo dokome Mosese deeyoko lamaiyuo, Embena kingi doko komau pee pingi dokona minyalyapala koko pyambunya leya. Leyamuli pyuo pipala neta nyuo kandeyamo dokopa rete rapa pyuo kewa lao pee lombakinyi peyo epeya.
\v 7 Epeyamo dokopa Kamongome deeyoko lao, Embena kingi doko komau pee pingi dokona kambako pyambuo kanda, leya. Leyamuli pyuo pipala neta nyiyamo dokopa yanenge mee karengenyili pyuo rali piyamo kandeya.
\v 8 Dokopa Kamongome lao, Nakamame yulu wambo doko kando kinyi lao suu pyaa narami ramo dokopa dee lapo pyuo pirinyi dakeme kinyi lao serami, leya.
\v 9 Embame yulu lama dolapo pirinyipape nakamame kando see nao dee embame lare doko soo nembeyami kande dokopa ipwa Naele epo penge dokona kamwapala yuu oo lasi dokona kulimbwape. Dokopa ipwa doko ranjama ingyuo epo para, leya.
\p 
\v 10 Moseseme Kamongo kando pii leyamo dokona lao kalyuo leya. Namba wambu malunya lenge kambu dokona sipurapala pii laa nange kandale. Dee yuu gii embame namba kando nyepala langi kande dokona piso pao dakepape laa naowako karo. Namba pii lalana saka napala mona palyuo ŋeŋe lao lenge leya.
\p 
\v 11 Dokopa Kamongome lao, Apimi wambunya nenge kata retakamiyase? Apimi renge kuiyuo kale poeyo pii pyakame soo pingisi? Apimi baa kandena lao lenge ranyi retope dee kwaeyo pingisi? Yulu dupwana pingi doko Kamongo nambaŋa.
\v 12 Dokona lao dakepa emba paaleŋe. Nambame emba nyiso dopa pyuo laa lao pyongo pyaro lyakande, leya.
\p 
\v 13 Dopa lao dake leyamopape Moseseme lao, Daa. Kamongo emba mendali wakale kapa lao suu pyarende pena lao nembape, leya.
\p 
\v 14 Kamongo baame Mosese kando imbu singi nyepala lao, Embena yangone Erone Lipae rara baa kara nalyase? Baame pii kapa lenge doko silyu. Doko dakepa baa emba kandala epelyamo. Baame rae maiyuo emba kando nyolopyamo.
\v 15 Erone laramo dupwa dopa pyuo lena lao embame lamairi. Lamairinyipa nambame nakamba laparae nyisaronopa pii lao yulu pirambi dupwana apa pyuo pirambi lao lasaka piru.
\v 16 Baame wambu dupwa kando embena lakara. Baa embena pii minyingi akali ingyuo karara. Dokopa embame Anatumi dopa pinya dapa pinya lenge dopale ingyuo lao karare.
\v 17 Pangali dake embena kingi raka dokona minyuo dokome yulu andake wambumi kanda nange dupwa piriŋi, leya.
\s1 Mosese Dee Kapu Kyuo Isipi Peya
\p 
\v 18 Mosesena imwange Jetero kareyamo dokona lambuo peya. Papala lao, Yuu Isipi dokona nambana wambu dupwa mende pii napyamo kapa karamipi lao kandala parowale, leya. Dokopa Jeterome kapaŋa pena leya.
\p 
\v 19 Leyamo dokopa Kamongome yuu Mitiane dokona epo Mosese lamaiyuo, Dakepa yuu Isipi dokona lambuo paaleŋe. Wambu emba pyalana piyami kande dupwa kumuo oteyami lyakande, leya.
\v 20 Dokopa Mosese banya enda wanepe nyuo mena donge dokona petena lapala lanyuo Isipi dokona lambuo peya. Dopa pyuo pao baa range Anatumi pangali maiyamo doko nyuo wakyuo peya.
\p 
\v 21 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo, Epapu emba Isipi pelene kande dokona wambumi yulu kanda nangende nambana porai dokome piriŋi lao jiyu kande doko Peraona lenge kambu dokona kandokondali pyuo pipi. Pirinyipa nambame banya mona doko kana pokaronopa wambu dupwa kaka soo yaki nyii nara lyakande, leya.
\v 22 Dokopa embame Perao lamaiyuo, Kamongo dokome dopa letamo. Isaraele rara dupwa nambana wane mupwa kyawalengya lao mandengeŋe.
\v 23 Nambana wane nakamame namba lakandena pena laka lapunupape embame kamba lao karene dokona lao dakepa nambame embena wane mupwasa doko pyao kumakaro letamo lare, leya.
\p 
\v 24 Mosese baa yuu Isipi panya peyamo katasa palimwa penge yuu andape dokona Kamongome Mosese kando nyepala baa pyalana piya.
\v 25 Dopa piyamo dokopa Mosesena etenge Sipora lenge dokome kana nenge karengendeme banya ikinyingi yanenge kalomakamipala yanenge dokome Mosesena kimbu doko warendakamiya.
\v 26 Yanenge kalomenge yulu dokona lao baame Mosese lamaiyuo, Emba nambana akalingi ingyapyamopape emba yanenge kalomenge akali dokonaŋa, leya. Dopa leyamo dokona Kamongome Mosese baa pyaa nao mee karena kaeya.
\p 
\v 27 Dokopa Kamongome Erone lamaiyuo, Yuu muiyane dokona Mosese epelyamoŋo kando nyela pena leya. Dokopa Eroneme Anatunya yuu kyau poo pyasi dokona kando nyela peya. Pao epeyamo kando nyepala Eroneme Mosese nyinyi piya.
\v 28 Dopa piyamopa Mosese Kamongome yuu Isipi pena lao karo dokopa wambumi kanda nange yulu pinya leyamo dupwa Erone polo lamaiya.
\v 29 Dokopa Mosese Eronepa yuu Isipi papala Ipuru akali mupwa dupwa nyuo malu palyiyambi.
\v 30 Dokona Kamongome Mosese lamaiyamo dupwa peparae Eroneme nakama lamaiya. Lamaiyamopa Moseseme yulu wambu kanda nange dupwa wambunya lenge kambu siyamo dokona piya. Doko kandapala wambu dupwame kinyilyamo lao suu piyami.
\v 31 Suu pyapala Kamongo Anatumi nakamana randa dupwa kandapala epamolyamo lao sepala nakama mona kando Anatunya kingi lakandeyami.
\c 5
\s1 Mosese Eronepa Perao Kandala Peyambi
\p 
\v 1 Mosese Eronepa Perao kareyamo dokona peyambi. Papala lamaiyuo, Isaraele wambunya Kamongo Anatu dokome nambana wambu dupwa nakama yuu muiyane dokona papala namba rape rape lao suu pyao nenge andake nengenyili pyuo nala pena lape letamo, leyambi.
\p 
\v 2 Peraome isingi lao, Kamongo doko baa angi apinde nambame banya pii soo Isaraele wambu dupwa pena larose? Namba Kamongo baa soo gisa nalyoŋo Isaraele dupwa pena laa naro daa, leya.
\p 
\v 3 Nakambame lao, Ipurumana Anatu dokome epo nambwa keta kando nyipyaŋa. Yuu remasa pao muiyane dokona namwana Anatu dokona lao mena pyao kiso maiyuo monale. Yaki nyuo kaeyape lao poraiyuo leyambi. Dopa pii narama ramo dokopa anga ikyane kiso joo yanda pimwai dupwame pinya lao nyuo suu lasara, leyambi.
\p 
\v 4 Isipi kiŋi dokome Mosese Eronepa kando lao, Nakambame akipamo wambu dupwa mata kara nembo dopa pyuo lambisi? Nakamba karapusi dupwa yulu pinginyili pyuo pela pena lalapape.
\v 5 Peraome pii kareta soo lao, Wambu dupwa wambu wai andake kisilyamo doko nakambame yulu yaki nyuo kaena lao lambisa pilyase? leya.
\p 
\v 6 Yuu gii mendaki dokonako Peraome banya akali Isaraele wambu pyalana pyuo yulu maingipi dee nakamana isingi akali dupwape kando lamaiyuo,
\v 7 Wambu dupwa wara nyuo yangi doko sukusa palyapala semene bange kana dopakale dee wasarami dokopa yangi mai napala range kota nyinya lamaiyalapa.
\v 8 Dopa pyuo dokopa kana semene bange wambo dokopa akipare wasingi kandalese lao dopaleko ingyuo manda manjo wasinya lalapape. Dee alowa pipala kuki pyuo wasaramiŋi doko daa. Nakama yulu pinya rae mai napala dokona Anatu kingi lao yuu muiyane dokona mena kiso maiyala panyaŋa lao karaminyi kande.
\v 9 Nakamana pii kyambo letaminyi dupwa sisaramiŋi dokona yulu ama poraiyuo maipala pyuo karena lalapape, leya.
\p 
\v 10 Leyamopa wambu pyalana pyuo yulu maingipi dee nakamana akali range dokona isingi akali ingyuo kareyami dupwame Isaraele wambu dupwa kareyaminyi dokona papala Peraome bange yangi dopale semeneme rambu lao reto anda pingi doko nakama jii naroŋo letamo.
\v 11 Dokona lao nakama rangeme yangi seramo kandaraminyi dupwa koto nyepala semene bange malu wasingi kandale dopaleko wasalapape, letamo, leyami.
\v 12 Dopa leyasa wambu peparae yuu Isipi dokona papyuo yangi dopale semene pakao reto pingi dupwa koto kareyami.
\v 13 Dokopa yulu maingi akali dupwame pyalana pyuo lao nakama yangi dopale semene rambu lao pingi dupwa nyuo jiyaminyi semene bange wasiyami kande doko suu pyao maluko ingyuo pena lao waso karalapape lao kareyami.
\v 14 Peraona akali Isaraele wambu yulu maingi dupwame Isaraele isingi akali dupwa pyao randa maiyuo kareyami. Randa maipala, Akipamo nakama kana semene bange malu wamba wasingi kandale dopale epapu wasa nalyamipi? leyami.
\p 
\v 15 Enakana Isaraele isingi akali karenge dupwame papala Perao piso soo lao suku lao, Akali andake emba karalendelamo akipamo embame namwa kando dopa pilisi? leyami.
\v 16 Dokopa yangi dopale jii nalyaminyipape semene malu wasinginyili pyuoko waso karalapape letaminyi doko akipamo letamisi? Dee dakepa nakamame namwa pyao karaminyi dokona kopetame doko emba keta palamo, leyami.
\p 
\v 17 Dokopa Peraome isingi lao, Nakama makalana wangu lakapala makalyaminyi renge dokona lao yuu muiyane dokona Kamongo lakando nenge rendamu pingi kiso maiyala pupwa laa lao piso soo karaminyi kande, leya.
\v 18 Dopa lapala Nakamana yulu dokona pila pupwape lao yangi doko jii naramaŋa semene wamba wasingi kandale dopako pyuo wasalapape, leya.
\v 19 Leyamo dokopa Isaraelena isingi akali dupwame semene wamba wasinginyili pyuo yuu peparae waso karalapape leyami doko kandapala randa nyilyamano lao soo manji nyiyami.
\p 
\v 20 Dokopa nakama Perao yaki nyuo papala Mosese Eronepa nakamana lao epo iso kareyambi dolapo kando nyiyami.
\v 21 Dokopa isingi akali dupwame Mosese Eronepa kando, Nakamba sipurapala mende piyambinyi dokona Perao banya wambu pipya namwa kando awa nalyaminyi. Dokona Anatumi nakamba kando kote lao randa mainyale. Nakambame namwa pinya lao wua nyuo kingi rakana palyakamyuo nyuo kisambisa pipya, leyami.
\s1 Moseseme Mona Randame Kumuo Anatu Piso Siya Doko
\p 
\v 22 Dee kambako Moseseme Kamongo lamaiyuo, Kamongo akipamo embena wambu dupwa kyawa yaki nyuo kaeyo randa mailipi? leya. Aki rengendena namba wambu dupwa kandala puu leese?
\v 23 Nambame Perao lamaiyakala epeyono dokona piso pao dakepape baame embena wambu dupwa mee randa maiyuoko karamo. Karapyamopape embame nakama nyisaroŋo laope mende ingya nalene, leya.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo, Dakepa nambame Perao kando mende pingi pyapono doko pao kandalale. Perao banya kingi porai dokome banya yuu doko yaki nyuo pena lapala wambu dupwa poraiyuo suu lanyi nembara, leya.
\s1 Anatumi Mosese Kee Leya
\p 
\v 2 Anatumi Mosese lamaiyuo, Kamongo doko namba lyakande, leya.
\v 3 Namba Anatu Porai Wakasa dokoŋo lao Aporakamemoo Aisake Jekope keta epo paneyo. Nambana kingi Yawai lenge lao rangeme sinya lao lamai nayo lyakande.
\v 4 Nakama yuu Kenane nakama mee upunili palima paenge ingyuo epo papiyami doko mairuŋu lao kana minyuo lalu lao leyo.
\v 5 Dopako pyuo Isaraelena rara dupwa Isipi akali dupwame karapusi pyaminyipa randa nao ingi koo palyuo karaminyi dokona kandapala nambana kana minyuo lalu lao leyono pii dokona suu pyaro karoŋo.
\v 6 Dokona lao embame Isaraele wambu dupwa lamaiyuo Kamongo doko nambaŋa. Nakama Isipi dupwame karapusi pyuo yulu nyuo suu lao joo karaminyi dokona nambame nakama karapusi yulu pyakamyuo karaminyi dokona kingi rekya lao nyero. Nambana kingi porai dokome nakama pyao rekya lalana pyuo karo dokome nakamba randa koo maipala nakama kyawa lete nyero.
\v 7 Dopa pyuo nakama namba rangena ingyuo nyepala namba nakamana Anatu ingyuo kararo. Dokopa namba nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome Isipi wambu dupwa randa joo kareyaminyipa moko nyii kande dokolyamo lao serami, leya.
\v 8 Dopa pyuo lao, Nambame yuunde Aporakame Aisake Jekopemoo mairuŋu lao kingi ketae nembo lalu lao leyono dokona nakama rangena kipungi inginya lao jero. Namba Kamongo doko karo letamo lao lamairi, leya.
\v 9 Dokopa Moseseme pii doko Isaraele wambu dupwa lamaiyamopape nakama karapusi yulu kopetame maiyaminyi pyuo karapala makame kumuo kareyami dokome pii doko soo nyii nayami.
\p 
\v 10 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo,
\v 11 Emba Isaraele wambu dupwa kingi raka lao yaki nyinya lao Isipi wambunya kiŋi Perao baa lamaiyala puu, leya.
\p 
\v 12 Dopa leyamopape Moseseme Kamongo lamaiyuo, Isaraele wambu dupwame nambana pii soo nembami kandapi doko doŋo dee Peraome apa pyuo nambana pii doko serase? Namba pii angingyuo laa nange kandapi, leya.
\p 
\v 13 Pii doko soo kaeyo Kamongome Mosese Eronepa lamaiyuo, Isipi wambunya kiŋi Peraomoo Isaraele wambu dupwape Kamongome Isaraele wambu yuu Isipi doko yaki nyuo lanyuo pupwa lapyasa epelyambano larambi, leya.
\s3 6:14-27 Lipaena rara dokona wai kiso nyuo Eronepa Mosesepa kareyambi. Dee Eronena para pyao nyiyamo wambu lapona kingi pyasi palamoko.
\s1 Kamongome Mosese Eronepa Kando Dopa Pinya Leya
\p 
\v 28 Kamongome yuu Isipi dokona Mosese lamaiyuo,
\v 29 Namba Kamongo doko, Pii peparae nambame langilyu dusipa minyuo pao yuu Isipi wambunya kiŋi doko lamaipi, leya.
\p 
\v 30 Dopa leyamo dokopa Moseseme Anatu kando lao, Namba pii lalana yakara pingi doko emba silini. Apa pyuo kiŋi dokome nambana pii serase? leya.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo, Kanda, nambame emba kiŋinya lenge kambu dokona Anatu yale inginyi pyambwaronopa embena yangone Erone dokome embena poropeta dopale ingyapala pii lamaiyakara.
\v 2 Nambame emba dopa pipi dopa pipi lao pii langilyu dusipa peparae pao Erone lamaipi. Lamairinyi dokopa baame pao kiŋi doko lamaiyuo, Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu doko yaki nyuo pena lena lara.
\v 3 Dopa piramopape nambame kiŋi doko mona pokanyi pyambwaro. Pyambwapala nambame yulu wambumi pii nange lapo pirunupape baame embena pii soo nyii nara.
\v 4 Dokopa nambame yuu Isipi range dupwa randa andake mairunupa nambana Isaraele wambu dupwa Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo paro.
\v 5 Dopa pyuo nambame nakama kanda soo pyaronopa Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo eparami. Dokopa Isipi range dupwame namba Anatu lao soo nyerami, leya.
\v 6 Mosese Eronepa Anatu leyamuli pyuo piyambi.
\v 7 Nakambame kiŋi kando pii lamaiyambinyi yuu gii dokopa Mosese baa ee kana akalisa mange lama karo (80) dee Erone ee kana akalisa mange lama ipisu rema (83) nembo kareya.
\s1 Eronena Pangali Isa Doko
\p 
\v 8 Kamongome Mosese Eronepa kando lamaiyuo,
\v 9 Peraome nakamba kando yulu andake wambumi pii nange mende nakamba keta porai renge palamo lao lasaka pyuo pipwape leya kande dokopa Erone banya pangali isa doko Peraona lenge kambu sera dokona pyao pyambunya lao lamaipi. Dopa piramo dokopa pangali doko pao kau ingyara, leya.
\v 10 Lapeyamo dokopa Mosese Eronepa Perao kareyamo dokona peyambi. Papala Anatu leyamuli pyuo Eroneme banya pangali isa doko Peraomoo banya yulu pingi akali mupwa dusipa kareyaminyi dokona pyao pyambuyamo dokopa doko pao kau ingiya.
\v 11 Doko kandapala dokopa Peraome banya soo gisingi akalipi pipu lenge akalipi lapo epena leya. Leyamo dokopa pipu lenge dupwa epapala nakamana porai dokome yulu dopaleko isingi piyami.
\v 12 Nakamana pangali isa dupwa pyao pyambuyaminyi dokopa pao kauko ingiya. Dopa piyaminyipape Eronena pangali isa dokome doloma peparae nao goe leya.
\v 13 Dopa piyaminyipape Anatumi kiŋi baame warombo see nara lao leyamuli pyuo Mosesepa Eronepa pii leyambinyi doko see nao banya mona kana pokapala kareya.
\s1 Randa Andake Lapo Yuu Isipi // Keta Epeya
\s1 Ranjama Doko
\p 
\v 14 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo, Perao baa ama porayapala wambu dupwa kingi raka lao pena laa nalyamo.
\v 15 Dokona yangama nakamba ipwa Naele pona dokona paraŋa dokona papala Perao kando nyerambi. Nakambame pangali isa kau ingiyamo doko minyuo papala ipwa kee kama dokona baa isaro karalapape.
\v 16 Dokopa embame kiŋi doko lamaiyuo lao, Ipuru wambu dupwa yuu muiyane dokona papala nambana kingi lakando kararami lao Kamongo nakamana Anatu dokome embame nakama pena lape lao puu lapyasa epo leto. Dopa lapunupape wamba langiyunu simbi simbi piinyi dopaleko ingyuo epapu pilini.
\v 17 Epapu emba kiŋi doko aki mende nambame piru doko kandapala embame namba apiŋi lao soo nyera lao Kamongome letamo. Kanda. Kusape dakeme ipwa ketae dokona pyaronopa ipwa doko alowa pyuo ranjama ingyara.
\v 18 Dopa piramo dokopa kau oma dupwa kumarami dokopa ipwa doko ama ai wakasa pyarasa Isipi range wambu dupwa kapa pyuo kamuo nalana saka narami lare, leya.
\p 
\v 19 Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Embame Erone lamaiyuo banya pangali isa doko nyepala yuu Isipi dokona ipwa epo pengepe ipwa epo pena lao suu nyingipi ipwa pete singipi dupwa peparaena ketae palyuo minyaro karena lamairi. Dopa piramo dokopa ipwa peparae ranjama ingyuo dee isa lukuluku pisinya ipwa singi dupwanape dee kana wasisinya ipwa petenge dupwanape opetaeko ranjama ingyuo yuu peparaene ranjama soo pira.
\p 
\v 20 Mosese Eronepa Anatumi leyamuli pyuo piyambi. Kiŋi Peraomoo banya yulu akali mupwa dupwa pipya kareyaminyi lenge kambu dokona Eroneme banya pangali isa doko minyalyapala ipwa doko piya. Piyamo dokopa ipwa dupwa alowa pipala ranjama ingiya.
\v 21 Dopa piyamopa kau oma ipwana singi dupwa kumuyami. Dokopa ipwa dupwa ama ai wakasa piyasa Isipi range dupwa kapa ipwa naa nayami. Yuu Isipi dokona ranjama dokome mee ree ingiya.
\v 22 Dokopa Isipi range akali pipu lenge dupwame epo yulu mendaki dopaleko piyami. Piyaminyipa Perao baa poraiyuo kaeya. Kamongome dopa pira leyamuli pyuo kiŋi dokome Mosese Eronepa pii see naya.
\v 23 Doo piyamo dupwana mendepe soo nyuo laa napala Perao banya anda kapu kyuo peya.
\v 24 Isipi range wambu dupwa ipwa epenge dokona kapa narami ingya nayasa ipwa marenge dokona apu rapala ipwa siyamo doko neyami.
\p 
\v 25 Kamongome ipwa piyamo dokopa yuu gii yanda ipingi nembo ipwa doko ranjama ingiya.
\c 8
\s1 Mungi Dupwa
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo, Perao karamo dokona pao dopa lamaiyuo, Kamongome dopa letamo. Namba lakandarami lao nambana wambu dupwa pena lakape.
\v 2 Nambana wambu dupwa pena laa nare ramo dokopa namba embena yuu dokona keta randa joo yuu Isipi peparae mungi peyaro.
\v 3 Ipwa Naele pona dupwana mungi malu piso kete pyapala lapo yaki nyuo embena anda dokona eparami. Epo embena luu palenge pandape embena ratepe dee embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwana andape embena wambu dupwa peparaena anda dupwanape eparami. Isare pete dupwanape borete wasingi penge dupwanape epo paliramiko.
\v 4 Dopa piraminyipa embape embena wambupi dee embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwa peparaena yongo dupwana pyakao epo pisirami lare, leya.
\p 
\v 5 Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Embame Erone lamaiyuo banya pangali isa doko nyepala ipwa epo pengepe ipwa epo pena lao suu nyingipi ipwa pete singipi dupwa peparaena ketae palyuo minyaro karena. Dopa piramo dokopa mungi dupwa ketae epo yuu Isipi dokona mee ree ingyara lare, leya.
\v 6 Leyamo dokopa Eroneme banya pangali isa doko ipwa peparaena ketae palyuo minyalyiyamo dokopa mungi dupwa ketae epapala yuu dupwa minyarambu nyiya.
\v 7 Dopa piyamopape pipu lenge dupwame pipu lapala mungi dupwa dopako pyuo yuu dokona epena lao piyami.
\p 
\v 8 Piyaminyi dokopa kiŋi Peraome Mosese Eronepa epena lao kee lapala dopa lamaiyuo, Kamongome mungi dupwa nyuo nembakana lao ateŋa lalapape. Dopa pirambinyi dokopa nakamana wambu dupwame mena pyao kiso Kamongo mairami lao nambame nakama pena laro, leya.
\p 
\v 9 Dokopa Moseseme Perao isingi lamaiya. Nambame rae maiyuo ateŋa lakaro. Embame yuu gii rombo palyarene dokona embape embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwape embena wambu dupwapena ateŋa lakaro. Dopa pirunu dokopa mungi peparae neta pao ipwa Naele dokona iki serami.
\p 
\v 10 Kiŋi dokome isingi lao, Rakya embame nambana lao ateŋa lakare, leya. Leyamo dokopa Moseseme lao, Emba piso silinyili pyuo piru. Pirunu dokopa anatu wakale mende Kamongo namwana Anatu dopakale daa lao soo gisare.
\v 11 Mungi dupwame embape embena wambupi embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwa peparaepe yaki nyepala ipwa Naele dokona iki serami, leya.
\v 12 Dokopa Mosese Eronepame Perao yaki nyuo peyambi dokopa Moseseme mungi dupwa kiŋi keta peteyamo dupwa nyisa nyuo nembena lao Anatu kando ateŋa poraiyuo piya.
\v 13 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese leyamuli pyuo mungi anda dupwanape anda kamapi ee dupwanape peteyaminyi dupwa kumuo pao siyami.
\v 14 Dokopa Isipi wambu dupwame mungi dupwa yapo nyuo kamba kamba malu palyuo reteyaminyi dokopa yuu dokona nyenenge ai wakasa piya.
\v 15 Piyamopa Perao baame mungi dupwa kumuo pao mee ingiyamo kandapala dokopa mona kamba kana poko poraiyuo kaepala Kamongome leyamuli pyuo baame Mosese Eronepana pii see naya.
\s1 Oro Dupwa
\p 
\v 16 Kamongome Mosese lamaiya. Embame Erone lamaiyuo banya pangali isa dokome yuu dokona pinya. Pyaramo dokopa sinjimu dupwa pao oro ingyapala yuu Isipi minyarambu nyera lare, leya.
\v 17 Leyamo pii doko sepala Eroneme banya pangali isa doko minyalyapala yuu dokona pyao pisiya. Dokopa yuu Isipi dokona sinjimu peparae dupwa alowa pyuo oro ingyapala mena wambupi yongo dupwana minyarambu nyiya.
\v 18 Pipu lenge akali dupwame dopako pyuo makande minyuo pinya piyaminyipape kapa ingyuo pii nayami. Nakamana menape nakamana yongope dupwa peparaena oro mee peteya.
\v 19 Dokona lao pipu lenge akali dupwame Perao kando yulu dake Anatumi pipyalyamo leyami. Dopa leyaminyipape Perao baa ama porayapala Kamongome leyamuli pyuo baame Mosese Eronepana pii see naya.
\s1 Wambena Dupwa
\p 
\v 20 Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo, Rakya wamba yangama Perao baa ipwa maresa paramo dokopa emba pao kando nyepala dopa lamairi. Kamongome dopa letamo, Nambana wambu dupwa namba lakandarami lao pena lare.
\v 21 Embame nambana wambu dupwa pena laa nare ramo doko kinyi kinyi langilyu nambame wambena malu mee embape embena wambupi embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwape keta peyaro. Peyarono dokopa Isipi rangena anda dupwanape yuu peparaenape wambename minyarambu nyuo sera.
\v 22 Dopa piramopa nambame yuu Gosane nambana wambu palaminyi dokona lili pyuo wambena peya naro. Dopa pirunu dokome namba Kamongo doko yuu dakena yulu pyuo karene lao nakamame soo nyerami.
\v 23 Nambame nambana wambupi embena wambupi komandapala yulu pii naro. Yulu wambumi pii nange dakeme rakya panda nyuo pira, leya.
\v 24 Kamongome wambena ama malu mee peyamopa Peraona andape banya yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwana andape siya. Dokona lao yuu Isipi peparae ama kokwa soo peya.
\p 
\v 25 Peraome Mosese Eronepa epena lapala lamaiyuo, Yuu dakena mena dupwa pyao kiso nakambana Anatu maiya pupwa, leya.
\p 
\v 26 Leyamo dokopa Moseseme isingi lao, Namwame yuu dakena mena dupwa pyao kiso namwana Kamongo Anatu mairama ramo yulu doko kapa ingya nara. Doko Isipi wambumi kandapala ipyarami. Namwame Isipi wambunya lenge kambu dokona mena pyao kiso mairama ramo dokopa nakamame rae mai nao ipyapala namwa kaname pyao kumakarami.
\p 
\v 27 Namwa yuu gii rema nembo yuu muiyane dokona pao karapala dokopa namwana Kamongo Anatumi langiyamuli pyuo mena dupwa pyao kiso mairama, leya.
\p 
\v 28 Leyamo dokopa Peraome dopa lamaiyuo, Nakama ama nanesa paa narami ramo doko nambame nakama yuu muiyane dokona nakamana Kamongo Anatu mena dupwa pyao kiso maiyala kapa pupwa, laro. Nambana lao ateŋa lakalapape, leya.
\p 
\v 29 Moseseme isingi lao, Mee mende usale namba papala rakya wambena dupwame embape embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwape embena wambupi yaki nyuo pena lao Anatu kando ateŋa lakaro. Dopa piru dokopa embame namwa dee minyoko pyuo wambu dupwame Anatu mena kiso maiya parami dupwa daa lao minyaro see napipi, leya.
\p 
\v 30 Dopa lapala Moseseme Perao yaki nyepala baa pao Kamongo kando ateŋa leya.
\v 31 Ateŋa lao Moseseme piso siyamuli pyuo Kamongome Perao banya wambupi banya yulu akali mupwa dupwape keta wambena dupwa rekya lao nembeya. Nembeyamo dokopa kuki mendepe ama pisa naya.
\v 32 Dopa pepeyamopape Peraome dee ama poraiyuo mona kana poko karapala Isaraele wambu dupwa kaka soo pena laa naya.
\c 9
\s1 Mena Kumuyami
\p 
\v 1 Anatumi Mosese lamaiya. Embame kiŋi Perao karamo dokona papala baa dopa lamaiyuo, Kamongo Ipuru wambunya Anatu dokome lao, Nambana wambu dupwame nambana kingi minyalyuo lao lakandarami lao pena lakape.
\v 2 Embame wambu dupwa pena laa napala mee minyaro sere ramo dokopa nambame randa andake anga yakane koo ree lapo
\v 3 embena mena dongepe ose kamele bulamakao sipisipi memepe peparaena peyaro.
\v 4 Dokopa Isaraele wambunya mena dupwape Isipi wambu dupwana mena dupwape liti pirunu dokome Isaraele wambunya mena dupwana mendepe kuma nara.
\v 5 Namba Kamongo doko yuu gii reto rakya piru lao lalu lao lapya lare, lao Kamongome Mosese lamaiya.
\p 
\v 6 Dokopa yangama Anatu leyamuli pyuo piyamo dokopa Isipi wambunya mena peparae kumuo oteyami. Dopa piyamopape Isaraele wambunya mena dupwana mendepe kuma naya.
\v 7 Dokopa Peraome piso soo, Apa pipyase? leya. Leyamo dokopa Isaraele wambunya mena dupwana mende kuma napya lao lamaiyami. Dopa leyaminyipape Peraome porayapala wambu dupwa kaka soo yaki nyuo pena laa naya.
\s1 Amungi Dupwa
\p 
\v 8 Anatumi Mosese Eronepa lamaiyuo, Isare pete dokona kingi laparaeme pee dupwa nyerambinyi dokopa Moseseme Perao karamo dorena ketae pyao nembara.
\v 9 Pyao nembaramo dokopa sinjimu kyau lenge dopakale ingyuo yuu Isipi peparaena raeyo para. Paramo dokopa mena wambupi peparae keta amungi pisipala poro lalya lana pipala rete andake pira, leya.
\v 10 Dopa lapeyamo dokopa isare pete dokona pee dupwa nyepala Perao kareyamo dokona pao kareyambi. Pao kareyambinyi dokopa Moseseme pee doko ketae nembeya. Nembeyamo dokopa pao mena wambupi peparae amungi pisipala poro lalya lana pyuo rete piya.
\v 11 Isipi range menge dupwa rete piya doko suu pyao nakama pipu lenge akali dupwa dopako piyasa siyaminyi dokome Mosese kareyamo dokona isingi dopako pyuo eparami ingya naya.
\v 12 Kamongome kiŋi dokona mona kana pokanyi pyambuyasa Kamongome leyamuli pyuo Mosese Eronepana pii doko soo nyii naya.
\s1 Randake Kapa
\p 
\v 13 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiya. Rakya wamba yangama sipurapala Perao kando nyepala dopa lamairi. Kamongo doko Ipuru wambunya Anatu dokome dopa lao, Nambana wambu dupwame nambana kingi minyalyuo lao lakandarami lao pena lakape.
\v 14 Yuu gii dakepa randa dake embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwape embena wambu dupwape keta iki eparande daa. Emba keta opetaeko epara. Eparamo dokopa yuu muu peparaena namba yale mende kara nange doko soo gisare.
\v 15 Namba nambana kingi ketae palyapala embape embena wambupi keta anga peyapuli doko nakama peparae kumuo otamili.
\v 16 Dopa pii napala nakamame nambana porai doko kandarami lao lasaka pyuo nakama mee lete karalapa lao kaeyo. Dokona lao wambu dupwame yuu muu peparaena nambana kingi nyuo ketae nembarami lao piyu.
\v 17 Dopa piyunupape emba range mupwa lao suu pyao lakandamili lapala nambana wambu dupwa pena lao yaki nyerende daa.
\v 18 Yuu gii dakepale rakyana nambame randake kapa ama romende epena laro. Wamba yuu Isipi dakena dopale mende epelyamo mare kanda nangende epara.
\v 19 Dopa piramo dokona embena mena bulamakaope dee bange peparae kamanda silyamo dupwape nyepala kapa kararami lao panda andakare mendena pao retena lamaipi. Randake kapa eparamo dokopa mena rara peparaepe akalipi pyakuiyuo kamanda kararaminyi dupwa kumarami lare, leya.
\v 20 Peraona yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwana lapome Kamongome pii leyamo doko soo pakapala nakamana kendemande dupwape mena dupwa kapa kararami lao andakare lanyuo epeyami.
\v 21 Dopa piyaminyipape wambu lapo Kamongona pii see napala menape kendemandepe kamanda mee karena kaeyami.
\p 
\v 22 Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo, Embena kingi doko yake dulunya kanda kanda pyambwarene dokopa menape wambupi nenge eena andenge dupwa peparaepe yuu Isipi dokona singi dupwana kapa kapa pyuo randake kapa epara, leya.
\v 23 Leyamuli pyuo Mosese banya pangali doko yake dokona pyalyiya. Pyalyiyamo dokopa Kamongome randa maiyuo yuu pele pyuo gala lao randake kapa peyo piya. Dopa pyuo Kamongome randake kapa romende yuu Isipi dokona peya.
\v 24 Dopa pyuo karo porambaiye andake minyuo randake kapa epo yuu pele pyuo gala lao pyuo porambaiye apunda ama andake wamba wambu yuu Isipi paleyaminyi dokopa mende dopale epa nange doko epo sulu siya.
\v 25 Yuu Isipi peparae wambu mena suwape bange peparae kamanda kareyami dupwa randake kapame piya. Isako dupwa pyao kumako dee isa dupwa pyao lakao piya.
\v 26 Yuu Gosane Isaraele wambu paleyami doko iki randake kapame pyaa naya.
\p 
\v 27 Doko kandapala kiŋi Peraome Mosese Eronepa lamaiyuo, Yuu gii dakepa namba koo pipu. Kamongo Anatu baa rolae pipyamo nambana wambu dupwa nambamoo koo pimwa lao polo leya.
\v 28 Kamongo Anatu kando ateŋa lakape. Yuu galape randake kapape doko namwa kapa nyepelyamanoŋo, leya. Namba lalu lao leto. Namba epapu nakamba yaki nyero parami dee ama pisi narami, leya.
\p 
\v 29 Leyamo dokopa Moseseme baa lamaiyuo, Namba taone andake dake yaki nyuo paparo dokopa aopa yake dokona Kamongo Anatu karamo dokona nambana kingi pyalyuo ateŋa laro. Dokopa yuu galape apunda randake kapape dupwa epa nara. Dopa piramo dokopa yuu muu doo silyamo dupwa Kamongonalyamo lao sere, leya.
\v 30 Dopa pipyamopape embape embena akali mupwape dupwa Kamongo Anatu mupwa lao suu pyao paka nalyaminyi namba silyu, leya.
\p 
\v 31 Puu lapya isa jingi dopale yalende bui rao isa bali jingi dupwa wambu pyuo poo rao oteyamopape randake dokome pyao parakwayasa rumbiya.
\v 32 Dopa piyamopape witi jingi enakana ingyuo poo renge dokome kuki mende rumbya naya.
\p 
\v 33 Mosese Perao yaki nyuo taone andake dokona nyisarena peya. Papala banya kingi yake dokona pyambuo Anatu lao ateŋa leya. Yuu gii dokopa yuu gala laa nao randake kapa epa nao dee apu epa nao soko piya.
\v 34 Yuu gii dokopa yuu gala laa nao randake kapa epa nao dee apu epa nao piya. Peraome doko kandapala deeyako koo pyuo banya akali mupwa dupwa pipya mona kana pokapala karo kaeyami.
\v 35 Kamongome Mosese keta lamaiyamuli pyuo Perao banya mona andarena kana pokapala Isaraele wambu dupwa pena laa naya.
\c 10
\s1 Aimbu Dupwa
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo, Embame kiŋi Perao kandala puu. Doko nambame akalimi pii nange yulu dopale nakama keta pinya suu pyapala baape banya yulu pingi akali mupwapena monarena kana pokanyi pyambuyu.
\v 2 Dopa lapala dokopa lao, Nambame yulu akalimi pii nange pyuo Isipi wambu kopyali minyinyi nembeyo doko nakamame dopa pyuonde piyaŋa lao nakamana wanepe dee wanena ikinyi kauwanepe dupwa keta arome pyao lamairamiŋi dokona piyu. Dokona doko Kamongo dokolyamo lao soo manjo nyerami, leya.
\p 
\v 3 Dopa lapeyamo dokopa Erone Mosesepa pao kiŋi doko kando dopa lamaiyambi. Ipuru wambunya Kamongo Anatu dokome lao, Yuu mange akipare dee nambana pii soo nyii nao kamba lao kararepe? Nambana wambu dupwame namba kingi minyalyuo lao lakandarami lao pena lakape.
\v 4 Emba nambana pii soo nyii nalu nao nare ramo doko rakya nambame embena yuu dokona aimbu polanyi peyakaro.
\v 5 Dokopa ama malu soo kaeyo pisiraminyi dokome epo yuu pandape minyarambu nyerami. Nyepala isa yoko nengepe lapo randake kapame pyao maleyamo dupwana mendepe yaparonge nyii naramiŋi lao nao otarami.
\v 6 Dopa pyuo epo embena andape embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwana andape embena wambu peparaena anda dupwape epo simbuo rangu paraŋa. Yulu koo dopale mende embena kauwange imbwangepe wamba dupwa kareyaminyi dupwana kanda nange doko pyaka soo pira ingilyamo letamo, leyambi. Leyambinyi dokopa kiŋi dokome kapu kyepala yaki nyuo peya.
\p 
\v 7 Dokopa banya yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwame kiŋi lamaiyuo lao, Yuu Isipi dake repeta kwaeyo para lao masa nalese? Yuu gii akipare namwa randa joo karase? Isaraele akali dupwa yaki nyuo nakamana Kamongo Anatu doko lakandaramiŋi pena lakamipi, leyami.
\p 
\v 8 Dopa lapala Mosese Eronepa kiŋi peteyamo dokona lanyuo epeyami. Epeyami dokopa kiŋimi lamaiyuo, Nakambana Kamongo Anatu doko range lakandala parami ingilyamo, leya. Dopa lapala piso soo, Paramiko doŋo apimoo angingyuo paramisi? leya.
\p 
\v 9 Dokopa Moseseme isingi lao, Namwa peparae paramanopa namwana wane dee alemo endemope opetaeko parami. Kamongo Anatu lakando banya kingi ketae pyambuo mena pyao kiso pati lao nao pisirama ingilyamo dokona namwame namwana wanenge ikinyingipi mena bulamakaope sipisipi memepe dupwa opetaeko lanyuo parama, leya.
\p 
\v 10 Dokopa kiŋimi lao, Enda wanepe opetae paa narami lao Kamongona kingi dokona lao kaeyapunu pilyamo. Daaŋa lapala lanyuo parami doko nakamame kopetame pirami lyakande.
\v 11 Ama daaŋa. Nakama panya suu piyami kande doko akali iki pao Anatu kingi lala parami, leya. Leyamo dokopa Mosese Eronepa kiŋinya lenge kambu siya dokona kara nana lao ralinyi nembeyami.
\p 
\v 12 Dopa pyuo leyasa kandapala Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo, Embena kingi dokome yuu Isipi silyamo dorena ingyuo pyambwapala aimbu nyinyi peyape. Dokopa aimbu dupwame epapala awa yoko isakope kyakange dupwa mende randake kapame yaki nyiyamo dupwa nao yuu rokwa lena leya.
\v 13 Dokopa Moseseme pangali isa doko minyalyiyasa Kamongome yuu dokona porambaiye yuu neta pyakaenge dorena piso korakama peparae minyuo pao kukwa peparae ingiya. Dokopa yangama aimbu angi dupwa nyuo soo epo malu palyiya.
\v 14 Dopa pyuo bii lao epo yuu liti dokona simbuyami. Wamba yuu mendepape aimbu yanda kambu dopale mende epelyamo kanda nange dee rengya dopa pyuo malu eparamo kanda naramiliko ingyuo kaiya karo epeya.
\v 15 Yuu sero kareyasa yuu dupwa kandalana saka nayami. Nakamame yuu dokona nenge isa yokope dupwa randake kapame pyao maleyamo dupwa kamame nao yuu rokwa leyami. Dopa pyuo nao dokopa isa jingi isana lyiyamo dupwa opetae neyami. Isa yoko nenge mendepe yuu Isipi dokona kyakao siyamo kanda nayami.
\p 
\v 16 Dopa piyasa kiŋi dokome yamarangyuo karo waiya lao Mosese Eronepa epena lapala lao, Nambame nakambana Kamongo Anatupi nakambape kando yanda pimwaiyuo kopetame pipulyamo.
\v 17 Epapu dakepa nambana kopetame pipunu doko nyuo kame sakana lao randa nao koo keta pali nara lao nakambana Kamongo Anatu doko kando ateŋa lao lamaiyakalapape, leya.
\v 18 Dopa lapeyamo dokopa Mosese baa kiŋi yaki nyuo pao Kamongo kando ateŋa lakamiya.
\v 19 Dokopa Kamongome dee neta pyakaenge dorena piso poo leyamo doko alowa pyuo neta yalyingi dokona piso porai ingyuo renge kuiyuo lapala aimbu peparae nyepala ipwa kota Kone lenge dorena soo kaki piya. Dokopa Isipi dokona aimbu mendaki mendepe pyarepala pao pisa naya.
\v 20 Doko kandeyamo dokopa Kamongome kiŋinya monarena kana pokanyi pyambuyasa Isaraele wambu dupwa dakepa dee paa naramiŋi daa, leya.
\s1 Yuu Iminjaro Kareya
\p 
\v 21 Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo, Embena kingi doko ketae palyapala yake dorena pyambwarene dokopa yuu Isipi dokona iminjo koro koro lara.
\v 22 Moseseme dopa piyasa yuu Isipi dokona yuu remasa lao iminjaro kareya.
\v 23 Dopa piyasa Isipi wambu range yango sukusa kandalana saka nayami. Dopa pipala andakare mee siyami. Dopa piyamopape Isaraele wambu paleyaminyi dokona mee yanga paupau lasi siya.
\p 
\v 24 Dopa piyasa kiŋi dokome Mosese epena lapala dopa lamaiyuo, Nakamana Kamongo mona maiyuo kingi lao pisa paraminyi doko kapaŋa dokona nakamana enda wanepe dupwa opetae pupwaleŋe nakamana mena sipisipipi memepe bulamakaope dupwako dae karena, leya.
\p 
\v 25 Dokopa Moseseme isingi lao, Doko kapalyamo. Namwana Kamongo Anatunylao mena yapasi lapo kiso maiyuo dee kiso mukinyi nembo piramano dokona lapo emba jere ingilyamo.
\v 26 Dopa piralyamo dokona dakepa namwana mena dupwana mendepe kara nana lao range nyuo parama. Namwame Anatu kingi lao kiso maiyuo pisiramano mena dupwa rangeme yapalyuo nyerama ingilyamo. Doko angi maresa paramano dokopa mena dokorekende pyao yangakaramiŋi lapyalyamo lao soo pakana palyarama, leya.
\p 
\v 27 Dokopa Kamongome kiŋi mona kana pokanyi pyambuyasa akali dupwa pena lao yaki nyii naya.
\v 28 Dopa pipala kiŋimi Mosese kando lao, Emba dasape kara nao popengeŋe dee kando laro ramo dokopa kumapengeŋe, leya.
\p 
\v 29 Dokopa Moseseme isingi lao, Emba kapa leteneŋe. Embame namba dee kamba kanda nareko, leya.
\c 11
\s1 Moseseme Wane Mupwa Mandeyaminyi Dupwa Kumarami, Leya
\p 
\v 1 Kamongome Mosese keta lao, Randa mende opetaeko lumwa pyuo Isipi kiŋi dee banya wambupi nakama mairuwale. Randa doko paparamo dokopa baame nakama kingi raka lao yaki nyolopyamo. Dopa pyuo nakama peparae ralinyi nembara.
\v 2 Dakepa embame Isaraele wambu dupwa peparaeme nakamana parali maki wambu dupwa lamaiyuo, Bange kana golomepe kana kulingimipi wasisi dupwa jinya lena lape, leya.
\v 3 Kamongome Isipi wambu nakamame Isaraele wambu dupwa kando mena suwape ingyuo suu pyaa nana lao piya. Dokona lao yulu pingi akali mupwa dee wambu peparaepeme Mosese baa akali andake wakasa lao suu piyami.
\p 
\v 4 Dokopa Moseseme Isipi kiŋi baa lamaiyuo lao, Epapu Kamongo dokome kukwama anda sukulya dokopa nambame Isipi sukusa dokona papiru, letamo.
\v 5 Dopa piru dokopa Isipi wambu peparaena wane kyawa dupwa kumarami ingilyamo. Kiŋi Peraona wane kyawa banya panda nyeramo doko kumaramo dokopa banya kendemande endame kenapa jingi pyao injingi dokona wane mupwa doko opetae kumarako. Dee mena bulamakao wambo kata pyao mandeyamo dupwa kumapengeŋe.
\v 6 Dokona lao yuu Isipi dokona ee lao kumaralerale dopale mende wamba ama laa nange dee rengyape laa naramilende pyaka soo larami ingilyamo.
\v 7 Dopa piramopape Isaraele wambu dupwa nakamana mena bangepe opetae suwa mendemepe dee wambumipi pyao koo keta palyarami ingya nalyamo lao serami. Namba Kamongo Anatumi Isaraele Isipipa kanya dokona liti pipyalyamo lao soo nyere, letamo, leya.
\v 8 Lapala Moseseme pii lao oto lumwa pyuo lao, Embena yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwa isale pao palipala namba mupwalyamo lapala nambape nambana wambu dupwape kala lanyuo puu larami lyakande. Dopa laraminyi dokopa namwa kapa yaki nyuo parama, leya. Dopa lapala Mosese imbumi kumapala Perao yaki nyuo peya.
\p 
\v 9 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese kando lao, Peraome embena pii see naraŋa. Renge dokona nambame yulu lapo wambumi pii nange dupwa konda pyuo Isipi yuu dokona pepalase lao dopale ingyuo para, leya.
\v 10 Mosese Eronepame yulu wambumi pii nange malu piyamo dupwa kiŋi lasaka piyambinyipape Kamongome kiŋinya mona kana pokanyi pyambuyasa kapa soo nyii napala Isaraele wambu nakama yuu Isipi yaki nyuo pena lara ingya naya.
\c 12
\s1 Pasopa Nenge Neyami Doko
\p 
\v 1 Yuu Isipi dokona Kamongome Erone Mosesepa pii dopa lao lamaiyuo,
\p 
\v 2 Kana dake nakambana ee kana dokona kana mupwa ingyuo pyaka silyamoŋo.
\v 3 Mana pii dake dopa letamo lao Isaraele wambu peparae lamaipape. Kana dakena yuu gii akalisa dokopa akali ree palu dokona larapu mena sipisipi yakane mendaki panda meme yakane mendaki larapu yapo nyinyale.
\v 4 Mena dokona ree palu dokome kapa nao ota narami ingyara ramo doko parali maki palenge dupwa role pyao piso nakama peparaeme menapa wambupa manda manjo mokwa soo maiyuo narami.
\v 5 Mena sipisipi panda meme mende nyepala kuiyuo naramiko doŋo, mena kali ene ee kana mendaki pasi dopale anga yakane palyuope rete pyuope pii nange doko nyerami.
\v 6 Nyepala kana dokona yuu gii akalisa ipisu kisima kukwa dokopa Isaraele wambu peparaeme mena pyarami.
\v 7 Wambu dupwame mena nala paraminyi anda dupwana mena ranjama lapo nyepala kambu konando penge dokona isa karenge dolapona kiso dee ketae isa lambuo palyingi dokona kiso pirami.
\v 8 Kukwama dokopako mena doko isareme yango narami ingilyamo. Nao dokopa borete isi pyambwa nange nenge dokope awa kyalyape kau pingi dupwa pipya kopo narami.
\v 9 Dopa lapala mena kyaka panda sanapengena kiso bolo pyapalape mende naa nao mena dokona kimbu ayembape ingi pungipi peparae kiso mukyepala narami.
\v 10 Dopa pyuo injisi lapo pyarepala pao yangama dokopa sisaraŋa nao otalapape. Injisipi lama siya kande doko isarena yango nembalu nembo nembarami.
\v 11 Dopa pipala nakama kata paraminyi dokona rapa rapa pyuo kimbu suu wapuo pangali isa nyuo minyuo panya lao suu pyao karo nenge waiya lao narami. Doko Pasopa Nenge nao nakamame namba Kamongo doko rape rape laramisa pira.
\p 
\v 12 Kukwa doo leto angi dokopa nambame yuu Isipi suku suku peparaena papyuo wane mupwasa dupwa peparaepe mena kali wambo mandenge dupwa peparaepe pyao kumakaro. Dopa pyuo pyao mee bange anatuŋu lao Isipi dokona lakandenge dupwa pyao nembo piru. Namba Kamongo doko karoŋo.
\v 13 Isipi wambu dupwa dopa pyuo pyarono dokopa anda kambu isa pote dokona ranjama yangasi dokome nakama palaminyiŋi lao panara doko kando pyaa nao yalo papa piruŋu.
\v 14 Namba Kamongome dopa piya lao suu pyao kame see naramiŋi dokona ee kana peparae yaka lao yuu gii dake dopa pyuo misi lao nenge nao nambana lao suu pyao pisirami, leya.
\s1 Borete Isi Palya Nao Nenge Yuu // Gii Doko
\p 
\v 15 Kamongome lao, Yuu yanda ipingi nyepo dusipana nakamame borete isi pyambuo wasingi doko naa narami. Borete isi pyambwa nao wasisi doko iki narami. Daaŋa lao yuu gii dusipana mendeme isi pyambwasi doko nao lara ramo doko nambana wambu ingyuo kara nana dokona yuu gii mupwa dokopa nenge isi nakamana anda singi dupwa peparae nyuo nembarami, leya.
\v 16 Yuu gii mupwa dokope yuu gii yanda ipingi dokona kambape nakama malu palyuo misi larami. Yuu gii dolapona yulu mendepe minyanda nao pisipala nenge dokoko iki rapa rapa pirami.
\v 17 Nakamana rara yuu Isipi piso yuu gii dakena lanyuo epeyaŋa lao kaeya nao misi lao nenge nenge yuu gii doko minyuo pyuo kararami. Ee kana peparaena yuu gii dake eparamo dokopa dopako pyuo karalu kararami.
\v 18 Kana mupwa dokona yuu gii akalisa ipisu kisima kukwa doko piso pao yuu gii akalisa lama ipisu mendaki dokona kukwama borete isi pyambuo wasisi doko wasaka pyuo kararami.
\v 19-20 Yuu gii yanda ipingi dusipana isi mende nakamana anda seramo kanda napenge. Daaŋa lao Juu rangepe dee wambu wakale mendemepe borete isi pyambwasi nara ramo doko nambana wambu ingyuo pisi nalyamo lao suu pyaroŋo, leya.
\s1 Pasopa Nenge Kanda Soo Neyami
\p 
\v 21 Moseseme Isaraele akali kyawa dupwa kyakale lapala dopa lamaiya. Nakamana ree palu dupwa Pasopa dokona nenge narami lao nakama peparae range wakale wakaleme mena sipisipi yakane panda meme yakane nyepala pyarami.
\v 22 Pyaraminyi dokona menana ranjama doko nyepala pere warake dokona retapala isa yoko lapo nyepala ranjama pere warake seramo dokona poeyapala pyarenda lanyi kambu konando penge dokona isa karenge dolapona kiso dee ketae isa lambuo palyingi dokona kiso pirami. Nakama dokona mendepe andakare yaki nyuo kamanda paa naraminyipa yangama inginya.
\v 23 Kamongome yuu Isipi sukusa papyuo Isipi wambu pyala pao isa ketae lambuo palyingi dee kambu dowa isa dolapona ranjama pisiramo doko kandaramo dokopa aŋala wambu pyao kumakara doko nakamana anda dupwana nakama pyao kumakala paa nana lara.
\v 24 Nakamape nakamana wane wanakepe dupwape mawa pii dusipa minyuo karalu kararami.
\v 25 Kamongome nakama yuu jeroŋo lao lalu lao leya kande dokona pao pyaka soo kararaminyi dokopa Pasopa nenge naowako pisirami.
\v 26 Dopa pyuo kiso nao pisiraminyi kandapala nakamana wane wanakepeme akinde lao piso seraminyi dokopa dopa pyuo isingi lao,
\v 27 Dokopa Nenge Pasopa lengende Kamongome Isipi wane mupwa dupwa pyao oteya dokopa Isaraele wambunya anda yaki nyuo kaeyo nakamana wane mupwa dupwa pyaa nayamo dokona banya kingi lakando ketae pyambuo namwame pilyamano larami, leya.
\p Dokopa Isaraele wambu nakamame pii doko sepala baa mupwaŋa lao kingi wapambupi lakao mona maiyuo lakandeyami.
\v 28 Dopa pipala pao Kamongome Mosese Eronepa pinya lamaiyamuli pyuo piyami.
\s1 Wane Mupwasa Dupwa Kumuyami
\p 
\v 29 Anda sukulya dokopa Kamongome Isipi wane kyawa dupwa pyao kumakao karo dokopa kiŋinya ikinyingi banya panda nyeramo wane doko pyao dee karapusi yuu anda koona paleyamo dokona ikinyingi mupwa doko opetae palepale pyao kumakaya. Dopa pyuo pyao karo dokopa mena wambo mandenge dupwa pyao kumakaoko piya.
\v 30 Kukwa dokopa kiŋi dee banya yulu pingi akali mupwape mee wambupi peparae lenge reyami. Lenge rapala yuu Isipi liti doko peparae anda mendakipi kaeya nao wane mupwa kumasi siyasa ee lao minyuo kaiya kareyami.
\v 31 Kukwa angi dokopako kiŋi baame Mosese Eronepa kee lao epena lamaiyuo, Sipurapala nakambame nakambana Isaraele wambu dupwa range lanyuo yuu dake yaki nyakao Kamongo doko kingi lao pisa panyaŋa leyami kande dokona pupwape.
\v 32 Nakambana mena sipisipipi memepe bulamakaope dupwa peparae nyepala yaki nyuo pao karo dokopa nambana randa dakena suu pyao elyape keta pisinya lao loma sakama pupwape, leya.
\p 
\v 33 Isipi wambu dupwame nakamana yuu doko waiya lao yaki nyii nao mona palyuo parami ramo doko kumuo otasaramaŋa yaki nyuo pena lao laokondali pyuo leyami.
\v 34 Dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwame palawa borete isi pyambwa nao wasalana rapa rapa pipala penge palawa yangaraminyi dupwana pyambwapala nakamana komaumi yake pipala soo peyami.
\v 35 Isaraele wambumi Moseseme pinya leyamuli pyuo Isipi wambu dupwame bange kana golomepe kana kulingimipi wasisi dupwape komau wasisi dupwape jinya lao piso siyami.
\v 36 Piso siyaminyi dokopa Kamongome Isipi wambu nakamame Isaraele wambu dupwa kando mena suwape ingyuo suu pyaa nana lao piyasa nakamame bange kee leyami dupwa kaeya napala maiyami. Dopa piyamo dokome Isaraele wambumi Isipi wambunya kamongonge bange peparae nyuo pao oteyami.
\s1 Isaraele Wambu Dupwa Isipi // Yaki Nyiyami
\p 
\v 37 Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Oramese piso kata nyuo yuu Sakote dokona panya yuu kata peyami. Peyaminyi dokopa akali ama malu (600,000) dee enda wanepe dupwa opetaeko peyami.
\v 38 Peyaminyi dokopa wambu rara wakale malu dupwape mena sipisipi memepe bulamakaope malupi opetaeko role pyao peyami.
\v 39 Kiŋi Peraome nakama waiya lao yuu Isipi yaki nyuo pena leyamo dokome nengepe palawa dokome borete isi pyambungi doko wasarami dokope wambo kapa rapa rapa pii nayami. Dokona lao nakamame yuu Isipi yaki nyiyaminyipa palawa borete isi pyambwa nange wasalana rapa rapa pipala soo peyaminyi dokome borete waso kisiyami.
\p 
\v 40 Isaraele wambu dupwa ee kana malu (430) yuu Isipi dokona palyuo kareyami.
\v 41 Ee kana 430 dusipa epo papeyamo yuu gii dokopa nakama Kamongona rara dupwa peparae yuu Isipi yaki nyiyami.
\v 42 Kukwama dokopa yuu Isipi yaki nyuo Kamongome nakama waa keta paliraminyi kandokondali pyuo nyuo lanyuo epeya. Kukwa doko Kamongo baa keta yuu rakyamepe pyamalyuo retapala doko mende piya kande lao Isaraele wambu dupwame suu pyao pisirami ingiya.
\s1 Nenge Pasopana Mawa Pii Lapo
\p 
\v 43 Kamongome Erone Mosesepa lamaiyuo, Dapwa Pasopa narami dokona pii dupwaŋa. Wambu rara wakale dokona mendeme epo Pasopa nenge narami doko nasaramiŋi daa.
\v 44 Kendemande mende nakamame ropo pyao nyiyaminde dokona yanenge wambo kalomakamirami ramo doko Pasopa nenge doko kapa nara.
\v 45 Wambu mende yuu gii malu role pyao kara naramo dokope panda wambu mende kana maiyuo nyepala yulu pyakana laraminyi dokope Pasopa nenge naa nara.
\v 46 Nenge angi peparae anda nenge rapa rapa pirami dokona narami lyakande. Kamanda minyuo paa narami. Mena akipi kisarami dokopa kuli dupwana mendepe minyuo roo pyaa narami.
\v 47 Isaraele wambu mendepe neta paa nao nakama peparaeme Pasopa nenge nao pisarami.
\v 48 Dopa pyuo naraminyipape akali yanenge kaloma nange mendemepe naa nara. Akali rara wakale mende nakama pipya palyuo karo nenge Pasopa doko kiso Kamongo ketae pyambuo naro leya kande dokopa wambo baape dee banya palenge akali opetaepe yanenge kalomakamirami. Kalomakamipala dokopa baa Isaraele akali dopale ingyuo nenge kiso Pasopa nenge doko nena larami.
\v 49 Wane dae manjisipi yuu rangepe dee rara wakale range nakama pipya role pyao karengepe dupwa peparae keta pii mendaki dokoko palira.
\v 50 Kamongome Mosese Eronepa kando yulu dopa pinya dapa pinya leyamuli pyuo Isaraele wambu peparaeme warombo soo piyami.
\v 51 Yuu gii dokopa Kamongome Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo epeya.
\c 13
\s1 Wane Mupwasa Dupwa Anatu Maiyami
\p 
\v 1 Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo,
\v 2 Nakamana wane mupwasa dupwa namba jipwape. Isaraele wane mupwa dupwape mena kali wambo manjisi dupwape nambanaŋa, leya.
\s1 Borete Isi Pyambwa Nange Nao Yalya Kando Peteyami
\p 
\v 3 Moseseme wambu dupwa lamaiyuo, Nakama Isipi karapusi karo neta epeyami kande doko dakepa suu pyalapape. Anatumi banya porai renge dokome nyuo lanyuo epeya kande doko yuu gii dakeŋe. Borete isi pyambwasi doko wasaka pyuo naa nalapape.
\v 4 Mange doo yuu gii mupwa kana mupwa Apipi lenge dokona yuu Isipi yaki nyuo epelyaminyi.
\v 5 Kamongome nakamana rora ambasupinya wambu dupwa kando Kenane wambupi Iti wambupi Amo wambupi Ipi wambupi Jepusi wambupi dupwa peparaena yuu jero lao kana minyuo lalu lao leya. Dokona lao baame nakama yuu amenge pingi dokona lanyuo eparamo dokopa ee kana peparaena kana mupwa dokona yaka lao nenge dake nao misi lao pipwape.
\v 6 Yuu gii yanda ipingi dusipana borete isi pyambwa nange narami. Doko napala yuu gii yanda ipingi dokopa malu palyuo nenge nao Kamongo lakando banya kingi ketae pyambuo pisarami.
\v 7 Yuu gii yanda ipingi dusipana borete isi pyambwasi dokona mende nasaramano lao wasaka pyuo pisipwape. Yuu liti dasipana isipi borete isi pyambungi mendepe see nana.
\v 8 Nenge kanda soo kiso karo dokopa Anatumi yuu Isipi yaki nyiyama dokona piso dopa pyuonde lanyuo epeyandena pilyamano lao angi doko nakamana wane dupwa polo lamaipape.
\v 9 Dopa pyuo lao reto nakamana enamba kinginyape puu pisapala kando karenge kandale dopale ingyuo paraŋa, leya. Dopa pyuo pirami dokome piyamiŋi lao panele laramopa Kamongona porainya renge dokome Isipi piso nyuo epeyaŋa lao banya mawa pii dupwa suu pyaro karo mana nyuo polo lao kararamiŋi.
\v 10 Ee kana yaka lao yuu gii rombo palyuo retami dokonako dopa pyuo yulu dake pipwape, leya.
\s1 Wane Kyawa Dupwa
\p 
\v 11 Nakamana rora ambasupi nakamape kando kana minyuo lalu lao leyamuli pyuo Kamongome nakama yuu Kenane dokona lanyuo epara.
\v 12 Dokona lanyuo eparamo dokopa nakamana wane ane mupwasa dupwa peparae Kamongo keta maiyalapape. Dee dopako pyuo mena kali wambo manjisi dupwa peparae Kamongo banya ingyara.
\v 13 Dopa pyuo dokopa mena donge kali dokoko sipisipimi panda nyinyale lao Kamongo maipala ropo pyao nyuo kaeyalapape. Dee daaŋa lao donge ropo pyao nyii naroŋo lao suu piyami kande doko kaepala mange doko minyuo koko pyalapape. Nakamana wane ane mupwasa dupwa dopako pyuo ropo pyao neta nyelapape.
\v 14 Rakyame nakamana ikinyingi dupwame doko akinde pilyaminyi lao piso siyami kande dokopa yuu Isipi dokona anjaro paleyamanopa Kamongona porainya renge palyuo moko nyiya dokona dopa pyuo karamano lao renge doko lamaipape.
\v 15 Isipi kiŋi dokome mona kana pokapala paa narami lao kamba leyamosa Kamongome yuu Isipi dokona mena wanepe mupwasa dupwa peparae pyao kumuo oteya. Dokona lao namwame mena kali mupwa mandenge dupwa peparae pyao kiso Kamongo maiyuo karamwanopape wane mupwa dupwa dee ropo pyao range laeyo nyingiŋi, lamaipape.
\v 16 Dopa pyuo lao reto nakamana enamba kinginyape puu pisapala kando karenge kandale dopale ingyuo paraŋa. Dopa pyuo pirami dokome piyamiŋi lao panele laramopa Kamongome banya porainya renge dokome Isipi piso namwa nyuo lanyuo epeyaŋa lao suu pyaramaŋa lao pingi ingyara, leya.
\s1 Kopa Isarepe Dolapome Kata Lanyiya
\p 
\v 17 Isipi kiŋi dokome Isaraele wambu pena lao yaki nyiyamo dokopa Anatumi ipwa kota nemba nemba kata soo yuu Pilisitia penge doko muu ingiyamopape dokona lanyuo paa naya. Renge doko nakama wambu yanda pimwai lapo katasa kandapala pako suu pingi alowa pipala yuu Isipi dokona dee pasaramiŋi dokona lanyuo paa naro lao Anatumi suu piya.
\v 18 Dopa pyuo parami dokona kaeyapala yuu muiyane ipwa kota Kone lenge dorena ingyuo lanyuo kyai mai pilya pyana pyuo panya peya. Peyamo dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwa yanda pela panya yanda kakupi nyuo rapa rapa pyuo minyiyami.
\p 
\v 19 Wamba Josepe Isaraele wambu kando pii lao kana minyingi ingyuo lamaiyakondali pyuo lao dopa leya. Nakama Anatumi yuu dakena kiiramo neta nyuo pao leya kande dokopa nambana kuli dupwa nyuo nakama yuu paraminyi dokona soo pupwape, leya. Dokona ingyuo Josepeme Isaraele wambu dupwa kana minyuo lalu lao lao lamaiyamuli pyuo Moseseme Josepena kuli dupwa nyepala soo peya. \fig Kata lasaka pyuo lanyuo paopiya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="13:21"\fig*
\p 
\v 20 Dokopa Isaraele wambu nakama yuu Sakote yaki nyepala yuu muiyane siyamo pinjingi dusa yuu Etame lenge dokona pao paleyami.
\v 21 Korakama dokopa Kamongome nakama dopa soo lanyuo pao dee kukwa dokopa isare rao kata lasaka pyuo lanyuo pao piya. Dopa pyuo nakama kukwa korakamape laparaena kata pena lapala piya.
\v 22 Kata nyuo peyaminyi yuu gii dusipana kopa dokome lenge kambu siyamo dokona kata lanyuo kukwa dokopa isare dokome kata lasaka pyuo pyuo lanyuo puu pao peya.
\c 14
\s1 Ipwa Kota Kone Lenge Doko Yalo Peyami
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao,
\v 2 Embame Isaraele wambu kando lao, Nakama kapu kyuo papala yuu Mikitole dee ipwa kota Kone lenge dolapona kanya yuu Piyairote dorena yuu Bealo Sepone repeta silyamo dokona palya pena lare.
\v 3 Kiŋimi lao suu pyao karo dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwame yuu muiyane dokona karo awali lao kata panya saka nalya saka nana pyuo karaminyi lao suu pyara.
\v 4 Dokopa Kamongo nambame kiŋi banya mona kana pokanyi pyambuo kararo dokopa baame nakama pyalana peta epara. Eparamo dokopa baape banya yanda singi dupwape pyao isa palyaronopa nambana kingi ketae para. Dokopa Isipi wambumi namba Kamongo lao serami, leya. Dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwame pinya lao leyamo dupwa piyami.
\p 
\v 5 Yuu gii dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwa neta pao kaeyamilyamo lao lamaiyaminyi doko sepala Isipi kiŋi banya yanda singi dupwamepe suu pingi alowa pipala lao doko akinde pyamase? leyami. Namwame kandakinya Isaraele wambu dupwa karapusi ingyuo namwana yulu pyakao karenge dupwa pena lapala kaeyamwanosa pyakao papelyaminyiŋi, leyami.
\v 6 Lapala kiŋi dokome banya mena oseme ipyuo yanda pela penge uliuli yanda singi dupwape nyuo rapa rapa piya.
\v 7 Rapa rapa pipala banya mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli dupwa peparae nyepala kata nyuo peya. Peyamo dokopa mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli dupwana ama keyange wakasa andete pakinyamange (600) dupwa banya yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwame rolo rolo pyuo minyuo peyami.
\v 8 Peyamopa Isaraele wambu dupwame namwame wini pyuo pelyamano lao rae maiyuo yaki nyuo peyaminyipa Kamongome kiŋinya mona kana pokanyi pyambuyasa baame Isaraele wambu dupwa rokeyakandeme imanji aku nyili lao peta ralyuo peya.
\v 9 Ipwa kota Kone maronge dokona yuu Piyairote dee Bealo Seponepa repeta pao palyuo kareyaminyi dokopa Isipi range yanda singi amipi mena osepe mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli piso yanda pela pengepe dee akali uliuli minyuo pengepe dupwame peteta minyaruli minyaruli pyuo epapala ralingi nyiyami.
\p 
\v 10 Dopa pyuo kiŋi dee banya amipi kimbu kingipi pyao piso epo pyala epeyaminyisa Isaraele wambu dupwame nakama kando yamarangupala Kamongome nyisinya lao kee leyami.
\v 11 Dokopa Mosese kando lao nembo, Yuu Isipi dokona malu anda mende see nangese? Yuu muiyane dakena namwa pyao kumanyi nembalana suu pyao embame lanyuo ipisi? Isipi yaki nyuo yuu muiyane dakena lanyuo ipi kandapi doko mendende pyuo ingyalana pilyamo kandape.
\v 12 Wambo yuu Isipi yaki nyuo epapa nayama dokopa dopa pisaraŋa lao langya nayamase? Namwa Isipi wambunya karapusi ingyuo kendemande yulu pyakamyuo kararamako karalapa lao yaki nyepala kaeya lao langiyama kande. Isipi dokona karapusi yulu lenge rao pyuo kararamano kakapu kokwaeŋe yuu muiyane dakena lenge ralu ralu kumalamano lamoŋo, leyami.
\p 
\v 13 Leyamisa Moseseme isingi lamaiyuo, Paka napala Kamongome apa pyuo nakama epapu kyawa lete nyilyape lao mee karalapa. Nakamame Isipi range dupwa dee kandaraminde daa.
\v 14 Kamongome nakamana lao yanda pyakalopyamo. Nakambame mende piraminde daaŋa, leya.
\p 
\v 15 Lapeyamo dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Akipamo embame nyisalipu lao kee letese? Embena wambu dupwa pelyaminyi dokona mee mende kamame lambuo pena, lamai.
\v 16 Lamaipala embena pangali doko kota pete dokona ketae palyaro karape. Dopa pirinyipa kota pete doko dulu kata dono kata pipala kee maro laramopa Isaraele wambu yuu oo lasi seramo dokona sukusa kapa kata parami.
\v 17 Nambame Isipi akali dupwana mona kana pokanyi pyambwaronopa nakamame nakama peteta parami. Dokopa kiŋipi banya ami yanda singipi mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli piso yanda pela pengepe dee banya uliuli minyuo penge akalipi nyuo isa palyaronopa nambana kingi doko ketae palira.
\v 18 Nambame angi pyao anamasi minyarono sepala dokopa Isipi wambu dupwame namba Kamongo doko karene lao soo nyerami, leya.
\p 
\v 19 Anatunya aŋala Isaraele wambu lanyuo wambeya doko nakama rekya lao matarena epo kareya. Dopako pyuo kopa soo kata lanyiyamo doko
\v 20 Isipi wambupi Isaraele wambupi peyaminyi kanya lili dokona epo siya. Isaraele keta rao dokopa kendali ingyuo yanga paupau lao rao dee Isipi kareyami dorena iminjanyi pyambuo soo piya. Dokopa paki pakipinya ami yanda singi kareyami doko kukwa dokopa mendalinya yuu dorena kapa pyuo epena saka nayami.
\p 
\v 21 Dokopa Mosesena kingi doko ipwa kota dorena ketae palyiyamo dokopa Kamongome neta pyakaenge dorena porambaiye ama porakai mende minyapala ipwa kota doko pyao soo peya. Minyuo pao yuu gii dokona kukwa peparaepe mende minyoko siyasa ipwa kota doko kaepala mee yuu oo lasi ingyuo siya.
\v 22 Dopa pipala ipwa doko lili pyuo wangu paki pakipi kame ingyaro kareyamopa Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu oo lasi mee siyamo dokona dumurena pakoeya piyami.
\v 23 Doko kandelyamano lapala Isipi wambu nakamana mena osepe mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli yanda pela pengepe dee uliuli minyingi akalipi dupwa peparaeme Isaraele wambu peteta kanda kanda kota pete oo lasi dokona ralingi nyela peyami.
\v 24 Yuu yangalana ene endenge siyamo dokopa Kamongome yake dokona kopa rakapana isare reyamo dokona kandaro karo Isipi wambu nakama yama luwasipwa pyaralyapala ii dupwa rombana puli pyao epeya.
\v 25 Dokopa baame mena oseme ipyuo pengena uliuli kimbu dupwa ipwa kee dokona yalyiyasa panya saka nayami. Isipi wambu dupwa doko mende piyasa kandapala Kamongome Isaraele wambu dapwa nyisapala namwa pyalyamoŋo dakena karo kaeyamana, leyami.
\p 
\v 26 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Embena kingi doko ipwa kota dorena ketae palyare. Palyarene dokopa ipwa dokome Isipi wambupi nakamana mena oseme ipyuo penge uliulipi dee dupwana minyingi wambupi nyuo yambe pyara, leya.
\v 27 Doko sepala Mosese banya kingi ipwa kota dorena ketae palyaro kareya. Yuu yangeyamo dokopa ipwa doko wambo singinyili pyuo siyamo kandeyami. Dopa piyamo dokopa Isipi wambu dupwa yalo neta imwali lao epeyaminyipape Kamongome nyuo ipwa kota sukusako pyambuya.
\v 28 Dopa pipala mena oseme ipyuo penge uliulipi dee dupwana minyingi akali dupwape Isipi ama yanda singipi Isaraele wambu peteta kanda kanda peyami dupwa ipwame nyuo yambe piya. Mendaki mendepe lete paa nana lao peparae yambe piya.
\v 29 Dopa piyamopape ipwa paki pakipi kipwa kipwa dolapona nyuo karalyaro kareyamo dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwa sukusa yuu oo lasi siyamo dokona peyami.
\p 
\v 30 Gii dokona Kamongome Isaraele wambu dupwa Isipi wambu keta nenge rekya lao nyiya. Nyiyamo dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwame Isipi wambu dupwa kee kama dupwana kumasi siyaminyi kandeyami.
\v 31 Kamongome Isipi wambu dupwa banya porai renge andake dokome pyao kumasiyamo doko kandapala dokopa baa mupwa wakasa lao suu pyao pakayami. Dopa pipala Kamongome angi mende kapa pira lao soo nyuo dee banya kendemande akali Mosese opetaepe soo nyuo piyami.
\c 15
\s1 Mosesena Kenane Pii Doko
\p 
\v 1 Mosesemoo Isaraele wambu dupwapeme kenane dake Kamongo dokona pyao leyami.
\b
\q1 Anatu baame mupwa wakasa dokome nyuo anamasi minyapya dokona lao Kamongo doko kando kenane dake pyaro.
\q1 Baame mena ose dupwape dee osena piso penge dupwape ipwa kota dokona pyao sukusa nembeya.
\q1 
\v 2 Kamongome namba porainyi pyambwapyamo porai ingyuo karo.
\q1 Baame namba elyape keta palyuo kiiramo nyiya.
\q1 Nyiyamo dokona baa nambana Anatu dokona nambame banya kingi lakandaro.
\q1 Baa nambana rakanena Anatu. Banya kingi andake dokona lao nambame lakandaro.
\q1 
\v 3 Kamongo baa soo giso yanda pimwaingi akali.
\q1 Doko Kamongo banya kingi.
\b
\q1 
\v 4 Peraona mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli dupwape banya yanda singi dupwape baame ipwa kota sukusa dokona pyao nembeya.
\q1 Banya yanda singi mupwa dupwana lapo yapasi dupwa ipwa kota Kone lenge dokona yalyiyami.
\q1 
\v 5 Ipwa kota yalu dokona yambe piya.
\q1 Nakama kamame ipwa kokorena kana petenge dopale ingyuo isa pao siyami.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 Kamongo embena kingi rolaerena poraingi renge doko ama mupwa wakasa.
\q1 Dokome yanda pimwai dupwa pyao poro lapala inji ranji pingi.
\q1 
\v 7 Embena porai wakasa mupwa ingyapinyi dokome embena yanda pimwai dupwa pyao nembelene.
\q1 Embena imbu singi renge doko wakasa palyapala yangi manda isareme renge dopale ingyuo wambu dupwa rao otelyamo.
\q1 
\v 8 Embame poo lapinyi dokona porambaiye dokome ipwa doko wangu dolapona karalyapala kame ingyuo londanyi pyambwapi.
\q1 Dokopa ipwa romo pyuo paenge doko anda apya dopale ingyuo roya karapya.
\q1 Dopa pipala ipwa pete yalu doko opetae porai wakasa ingyapya.
\q1 
\v 9 Dokopa yanda pimwai dokome lao, Nambame nakama peteta epapala nakama minyarapala nyero.
\q1 Nambame bange nakamana dupwa wakale liti pira pira pipala namba nyelana maserono bange dupwa nyero.
\q1 Nambana wua gela kolo nyepala dokopa nambana porai dokome nakama bange peparae retaraminyi doko nyero, lapya.
\q1 
\v 10 Dopa pipyamopape embame yuu mendaki ŋee soo poo lapi dokopa ipwa kota dokome wambu dupwa yambe pyapya.
\q1 Ipwa pete paka pingi dokona kenda kenda pisi bange yalyingi dopale ingyuo yalyiyami.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 Kamongo, anatuŋu lenge dupwana mende emba yalese?
\q1 Api mupwa wakasa poo pyasi emba yalese?
\q1 Api emba yalendeme yulu wambumi kapa pii nange dupwa pyuo yulu pakaramili porai dupwa pyuo pirase?
\q1 
\v 12 Embena kingi rolaerena pyasinju laro karene dokopa
\q1 yuu dokome namwana yanda pimwai wambu dupwa nao goe lao oteya.
\q1 
\v 13 Embena wambu kiiramo nyiinyi dupwa embena pii lao kana minyuo leene doko reto kaeya napala dokona palyuo mondo koo lao laminyii.
\q1 Embena porai dokome wambu dupwa laminyuo yuu yapasi dokona pee.
\q1 
\v 14 Dokopa wambu dupwame sepala nakama yamarangyuo pakame kumulyaminyi.
\q1 Enda wane manjinya pingi dokopa randa nyingi dopale ingyuo Pilisitia wambu dupwa randa nyuo pakalyaminyi.
\q1 
\v 15 Yuu Itome karenge wambunya akali mupwa dupwa pakame kumulyaminyi.
\q1 Moape range akali porai dupwa walu walu lao pungwa pungwa pilyaminyi.
\q1 Wambu peparae yuu Kenane palenge dupwa nakamana porainya renge pao otelyamo.
\q1 
\v 16 Walu lao pakange renge dupwa nakama keta palamo.
\q1 Embena porainya renge wakasa palipyamo dokona
\q1 nakama romo pii nao isa karele letaminyi.
\q1 O Kamongo, embena wambu dupwame pakiki palyama mee parami.
\q1 Dee embena wambu angi range kulisa embame kiiramo nyipinyi dupwa dopako pyuo parami.
\q1 
\v 17 Embame wambu dupwa lanyuo epo embena yuu kyau dokona wara pinyi palyare.
\q1 Kamongo, yuu doko embena anda piinyi mare doko.
\q1 Tembole anda Kamongo emba range yeelyo piinyi doko.
\q1 
\v 18 Kamongo emba yuu peparae kiŋi ingyuo karalu karare.
\s1 Miriamena Kenane Doko
\p 
\v 19 Isaraele wambu wambo ipwa kotana peyami dupwa ipwa kota karalyapala yuu oo lasi siyamo dokona sukusa peyami. Dopa pyuo peyaminyipape Peraona mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli dupwape dee dupwana minyingi dupwape ipwa kota sukusa peyaminyi dokopa Kamongo dokome ipwa doko nyuo pyasiya dokopa ipwa dokome nakama dupwa yambe piya.
\p 
\v 20 Poropeta enda Miriame Eronena pemalenge doko laikuli kuki mende nyiya. Dokopa enda peparae laikuli kuki lapo nyepala banya matarename pao karo laikuli pyao danjiŋi piyami.
\v 21 Miriame baame nakamana kenane pyakamiya.
\q1 Koo andake dupwa nyuo anamasi minyapya dokona Kaomongo banya kingi lakando kenane pyamanale.
\q1 Baame mena ose dupwape osena piso penge akali dupwape ipwa kota dokona sukusa pyao nembapya,
\m leya.
\s1 Ipwa Kau Pingi Doko
\p 
\v 22 Moseseme Isaraele wambu dupwa ipwa kota Kone lenge doko yaki nyuo lanyuo peya. Peyamo dokopa nakama yuu muiyane Sua lenge dokona peyami. Pao yuu gii rema nembo yuu muiyane dokona kata pao kareyaminyipape ipwa mende epeyamo kanda nayami.
\v 23 Kanda napala yuu kingi Mara lenge dokona epo ipwa kau pingi mende kando nyiyami. Dokopa nakama ipwa doko rende pii nalu nao nayamosa nakama naa napala kaeyami. Renge dokona yuu doko kingi Mara leyami. (Juunya pii lenge doko kingi Mara doko kau pingi dopale lenge.)
\v 24 Wambu dupwame Mosese kando mumu andake lao piso siyami. Namwa ipwa aki naramase? leyami.
\v 25 Dopa leyaminyi dokopa Moseseme Kamongo doko kando poraiyuo ateŋa piya. Piyamo dokopa Kamongo dokome baa isa mende lasaka piya. Dokopa baame isa doko nyepala ipwa dokona sukusa pyao nembeya. Nembeyamo dokopa ipwa doko mee rende pyuo rali piya. Dokona Kamongo dokome nakama mawa pii maiya. Maiyuo dee nakama makande pyuo kandoko piya.
\v 26 Baame dopa leya. Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatu doko nakamame kamba laa nalu nao napala nambame rolae lao suu pilyu dokona palyuo pyuo nambana dopa pipenge laro dupwa dopa lalyane lao soo nambana mawa pii dupwa minyarami ramo doko nambame nakamba Isipi wambu anga yakane kiso maiyunuli pyuo nakama jii naro. Namba doko Kamongo nakama pyuo lete nyilyuŋu doko karo.
\p 
\v 27 Enakana nakama yuu Ilimi dokona ipwa guu lenge akalisa ipisu lama epo dee isa bona akalisa yanda ipingi nyepo karo pingi dokona ipwa repeta dokona nakama epo anda pyuo paleyami.
\c 16
\s1 Nenge Myanape Dee Yakape
\p 
\v 1 Isaraele wambu rara peparae yuu Ilimi dokona yaki nyiyami. Yaki nyepala yuu Isipi piso pao kana lamana yuu gii akalisa ipisu kingi paki dokopa nakama yuu muiyane kingi Sini lenge doko yuu Ilimi Sainaipana kanya dokona singi dokona epeyami.
\v 2 Epapala yuu muiyane dokona karo nakama peparaeme Mosesepa Eronepa kando mumu andake leyami.
\v 3 Lao dokopa dopa leyami. Namwa yuu Isipi dokona kareyamano dokopa Kamongome pyao kuma siyali doko kapa ingiyali. Dokona namwa lambo lao pisapala mena minjupi nenge rara wakalepe nalana masiyamano doko peparae neyama. Dopa piyamanopape epapu nakambame namwa yuu muiyane dakena lanyuo epapala lopome kumanyi nembelyambinyi, leyami.
\p 
\v 4 Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo, Epapu nambame nakama peparae nenge yake panda piso apunda epenge dopale ingyuo jero dokona wambu dupwa nakamame yuu peparae yuu gii mendaki lao nenge kapa naramili pyuo nyela papa pirami. Dopa pirunu dokona nakamame nambana mana pii lasi dokona moko minyuo pilyamipi lao makande pyuo kandaro.
\v 5 Yuu gii mange pyakambwaro dokopa nakamame yuu gii lamasa lao nenge yapo nyepala rapa rapa pirami.
\p 
\v 6 Dokona Mosese Eronepame Isaraele wambu dupwa lamaiyuo, Kamongo dokome nakama yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo epeya lao epapu kukwa soo gisarami.
\v 7 Lao dokopa Kamongona yanga paupau lenge doko rakya yangama kandarami. Dokona nambwame Anatumi dopa pipwa dopa pipwa langiyamuli pyuo piyambano dokona nakamame nambwa kando mumu lao karo nakamame Anatu kando mumu leyamisa piya. Dokona nakamame Anatu baa kando mumu leyaminyi doko baame soo oteya, leyambi.
\v 8 Moseseme nakama lamaiyuo, Kamongo dokome nakamame baa kando mumu andake leyaminyi dokona kando soo otapala kukwa minju narami dokona joo yangama borete naraminyili pyuo joo pira. Nakamame nambwa kando mumu leyaminyi doko Kamongo kando mumu leyamisako piya.
\p 
\v 9 Dopa lapala Moseseme Erone lamaiyuo, Wambu nakamana mumu leyaminyi doko Kamongo dokome soo oteyaŋa dokona wambu dupwa peparae banya lenge kambu dokona epo karena lamaipi, leya.
\v 10 Eroneme wambu dupwa peparae lamaireyamo dokopa nakama kapu kyepala yuu muiyane dorena kandaro kareyaminyipa Kamongona yanga paupau lenge doko kopa rakapana paneya.
\v 11 Paneyamo dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo,
\v 12 Namba Isaraele wambu dupwame mumu laminyi silyuŋu dokona pii dake lamaipi. Alemanji kone pupuripi dokopa minju narami dee wamba yangama dokopa borete nalana suu pilyaminyi dupwa peparae narami. Dokopa namba Kamongo doko nakamana Anatuŋu lao soo nyerami, leya.
\p 
\v 13 Alemanji kone pupuripi dokopa yaka kuki dupwa bii lao epapala yuu paleyaminyi dokona bwaa lepa minyiya. Dee yangama dokopa paleyaminyi yuu dokona pipyae raiya peteya.
\v 14 Pipyae doko olo oteyamo mee wakakinya yuu dokona nenge myana kuki rekya lasi keyange doko siya.
\v 15 Dopa piyamo dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwame kandapala doko aki bange lao soo gisa napala mendali pisara pisara pyuo, Doko aki bangese? leyami.
\p Dokopa Moseseme nakama lamaiyuo, Dake nenge Kamongome nakama narami lao jipyaŋa doko.
\v 16 Kamongo dokome mawa pii lao, Nakama mendaki mendaki lao naraminyili pyuo nyuo malu palyarami. Palyaraminyi dokopa wambu ree palu dokona mendaki mendaki lao sikyali lita lama larapu nyerami, leya.
\p 
\v 17 Dokopa leyamuli pyuo Isaraele wambu lapome nenge malu nyiyami. Dee lapome kuki lama yeelyo nyiyami.
\v 18 Dopa pyuo nyepala makande piyaminyi dokopa malu mee nyiyaminyi dupwa kamame andakya naya. Dee lapo kuki lama nyiyaminyi dupwa kamame kukya naya. Nakama naraminyili pyuo manda manjo yapo nyiyami.
\v 19 Dokopa Mosese baame nakama lamaiyuo, Nenge yangamana narami dokona mendepe mendeme reta napala nao ote pinya, leya.
\v 20 Dopa leyamopape nakama wambu lapome Mosesena pii see nayami. See napala nenge lapo yangama narama lapala reto kaeyami. Dokona yangamarena nenge reteyaminyi dupwana kimwakapa pyapala ama nyenenge ai piya. Dopa piyaminyisa Moseseme nakama kandapala imbwaya.
\v 21 Yangama peparae yaka lao nakama nenge naraminyili pyuo nyuo malu palyara piyami. Dokopa neta rao andakiyamo dokopa nenge lapo pyarepala pao siyamo dupwa lili lao peya.
\p 
\v 22 Yuu gii pakinyamange dokopa nakamame nenge yuu gii lama napengele makande manjo wambu mendakinyi suu pyao lita kisima ingyuo nyuo malu palyiyami. Dopa piyaminyi dokona akali mupwa wambu dupwa iso kareyaminyi dupwame epapala Mosese kando lamaiyami.
\v 23 Lamaiyaminyi dokopa baame nakama dopa lamaiya. Dake Kamongo dokome dopa lao mawa pii reteya. Reteyamo dokona rakya yuu gii mupwa dokopa imambu soo Kamongona kingi iki lakandenge. Nenge mee isarena kisaramili dupwa kiso dee sanepena kisaramili dupwa kiso pipwape. Piraminyipa neta kakana pao siya kande dupwa wakale retapala rakya narami.
\v 24 Dokopa Mosese lamaiyamuli pyuo nenge kakana peyamo dupwa rakyana lao reteyaminyi dupwa rumbyuo kimwakapa pyaope pii naya.
\v 25 Moseseme nakama lamaiyuo, Epapu koro petenge yuu gii dake imambu soo Kamongona kingi lakandenge dokona nenge dake nalapape. Nenge lapo kamanda dokona seramo kando nyii narami.
\v 26 Yuu gii pakinyamange dusipana nenge nyuo malu palyarami. Palyapala yuu gii yanda ipingi dokopa imambu soo Kamongona kingi lakandenge dokome yuu dokona nenge yapo nyerami lao see nara, leya.
\p 
\v 27 Yuu yanda ipingi nyepo dokopa wambu lapo nenge yapo nyela peyami. Peyaminyipape dupwame dokona mende yoko pongo siyamo kando nyii nayami.
\v 28 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Yuu gii akipare nembo nakama wambu dupwame nambana mawa pii kamba laramisi?
\v 29 Namba Kamongo dokome yuu gii imambu serami doko jipu kandapi doko silyaminyi. Dokona lao yuu gii pakinyamange dokopa nenge kapa yuu gii lamasa napenge jero. Yuu gii yanda ipingi nyepo dokopa wambu peparae mendali banya anda yuupi yaki nyuo paa narami ingilyamo, leya.
\v 30 Dokona lao wambu dupwa yuu gii yanda ipingi nyepo dokopa yulu pii nayami.
\p 
\v 31 Isaraele wambu dupwame nenge doko kingi myana leyami. Leyaminyi doko ee waingi kuki kewa lenge dopale. Angi doko bisikiti amburali ipwangeme wasisi rende pingi dopale.
\v 32 Moseseme lao, Dake Kamongo dokome mawa pii ingyuo reto lao, Nambame yuu Isipi yaki nyuo yuu muiyane dokona lanyuo epo nenge jiyunu doko nakamana para pyao manjiraminyi dupwame kandarami lao nenge myana lapo nyuo retalapape letamo, leya.
\v 33 Lapala Moseseme Erone lamaiyuo, Nenge myana sikyali lita lama makande manjo nyuo pee kaname wasisi dokona pyambuo retare. Doko namwana para pyao manjiraminyi dupwame kandarami lao Kamongona lenge kambu dorena retare, leya.
\v 34 Kamongome Mosese mawa pii lamaiyamuli pyuo Eroneme Anatunya Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote dokona lenge kambusa au pyuo sera lao reteya.
\v 35 Dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwa ee kana akalisa kisima nembo nenge myana dokoko nao karo pao yuu Kenane kando nyepala palyuo kareyami.
\v 36 (Yuu gii dokopa sikyali kuki makande pingi dokome lita lama ingiya. Sikyali doko botole andake mendena pyambuo simbuya dopale. Dee sikyali andake makande pingi dokome lita akalisa lama dopale ingyuo jerame mendena pyambuo simbuya.)
\c 17
\s1 Kana Dokona Ipwa Guu Lao Potemeya
\r (Nam 20:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Isaraele wambu dupwa peparae yuu muiyane kingi Sini lenge doko yaki nyepala Kamongome leyamuli pyuo yuu mendasa palipa mendasa palipa pyuo peyami. Papala yuu Orepitimi dokona palyuo kareyaminyipape yuu dokona wambu dupwa ipwa narami lao mende epa naya.
\v 2 Dopa piyamosa Mosese kando nakamame mumu andake lao ipwa nalana jinya, leyami.
\p Leyaminyi dokopa Moseseme isingi lao, Akipamo namba kando mumu letamisi? Akipamo nakamame Kamongo doko kando makande pilyamisi? leya.
\p 
\v 3 Dokopa wambu dupwa ipwa nano wakasa piyasa Mosese kando mumu andake leyami. Akipamo embame namwa yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo epeese? Dokona namwape wane wanakepe menape ipwa nanapala kumarami lapala piisi? leyami.
\p 
\v 4 Dokopa Moseseme Kamongo poraiyuo loma siya. Nambame wambu dapwa apa pirusi? Nakamame namba oo repeta kaname pyalana pilyaminyi, leya.
\p 
\v 5 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo dopa lao, Wambu dupwa enakana lapala Isaraele akali mupwa dupwana lapo wambo kyawa nyuo lanyuo pupi. Pao dokopa pangali isa ipwa Naele piinyi doko opetae nyuo minyuo pupi.
\v 6 Yuu kyau Sainai mare dokona kana mendena namba embena lenge kambusa kararo. Kararono dokopa kana doko pangalimi pyare dokopa wambu dupwa ipwa narami lao guu lao potemara, leya. Dokopa Isaraele akali mupwa dupwa kando kareyaminyipa Moseseme kana doko pangali dokome piya.
\p 
\v 7 Isaraele wambu dupwame Kamongo doko kando makande pyuo mumu lao lao, Kamongo doko namwa pipya role pyao kara panda daase? leyaminyi dokome Moseseme yuu doko kingi lama Masa dee Merepa, leya. (Kingi Masa doko makande pingi dopale. Dee kingi Merepa doko mumu lenge dopale.) \fig Kareyambinyipako pao neta anda pendo leya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="17:12"\fig*
\s1 Amaleke Wambu Pipya Yanda Piyami
\p 
\v 8 Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Orepitimi dokona paleyaminyipa Amaleke wambu dupwame pyala epeyami.
\v 9 Epeyaminyi dokopa Moseseme Josua lamaiyuo lao, Rakya Amaleke wambu pyala parami lao akali lapo rombo palyakare. Palyakarene dokopa namba yuu kyau manda dokona Anatumi pangali jiyamo doko minyaro kararo, leya.
\v 10 Josua baa Moseseme lamaiyamuli pyuo Amaleke wambu pyala peyamo dokopa Mosese Erone Uamoo yuu kyau dokona ketae peyami.
\v 11 Peyaminyi dokopa Mosese banya kingi doko ketae palyaro kareyamo dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwame mupwa ingyuo anamasi minyiyami. Dopa piyaminyipape Mosese banya kingi isa yaki nyiyamo dokopa Amaleke wambu dupwa mupwa ingyuo kanda soo wini pyuo piyami.
\v 12 Piyaminyi dokopa Mosese banya kingi dolapo kele neyamo dokopa Erone Uapa kana mende baa isa petena lao nyuo reteyambi. Reteyambinyi dokopa baa ketae dokona peteyamo dokopa nakamba wangu wangu pyuo karapala banya kingi minyalyaro kareyambi. Kareyambinyipako pao neta anda pendo leya.
\v 13 Dopa piyaminyi dokome Josuame Amaleke wambu dupwa yaka lao pyao oteya.
\p 
\v 14 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Wambu dupwame suu pyaramiŋi lao dopa pyuo Amaleke wambu pyao anamasi minyiyamaŋa lao arome pyaramiŋi sinju pii pyao retape. Dee Josua lamaiyuo, Nambame Amaleke wambu dupwa kingi see nana lao pyao nembalu nembo nembaro lapya lape, leya.
\v 15 Moseseme mena pyao kiso maingi kana pyare mende wasiya. Wasapala Kamongo doko nambana Palake dopale ingilyamo lao kingi leya.
\v 16 Lao dokopa Kamongona palake doko ketae palyuo minyalyarami. Dokopa Kamongo dokome Amaleke wambu dupwa pyao karalu karara, leya.
\c 18
\s1 Jetero Baame Mosese Kandala Peya
\p 
\v 1 Jetero baa Mosesena imwange yuu Mitiane dokona purisi ingyuo karenge dokome Anatumi Mosesemoo banya Isaraele wambu dupwa peparaepe nyiso yuu Isipi yaki nyuo mondo lao lanyuo epeyamo doko sepala kandala epeya.
\v 2 Mosesena etenge Sipora lenge doko banya yuusa petena lapala peyamo doko banya imwange Jetero dokome lanyakamyuo epeya.
\v 3 Jeterome Siporana ikinyingi Gasome Eliasepa dolapo opetaeko lanyakamyuo epeya. Moseseme namba upunili ingyuo yuu wakalemana dokona karapu lapala banya wane mende kingi Gasome leya. (Kingi Gasome doko upunili dopale lenge.)
\v 4 Kiŋi Perao dokome pyao randa jii nana lapala nambana rakangena Anatu dokome namba nyiso kyawa minyiya. Lapala banya wane mende dokona kingi Eliase leya. (Kingi Eliase doko Anatumi namba nyisingi dopale lenge.)
\v 5 Mosese baa Anatunya yuu kyau poo pyasi dokona paleyamo dokona Jeterome banya wanenge dokope dee banya kauwange wane dolapope yuu muiyane dokona lanyakamyuo epeya.
\v 6 Jeterome wambo Mosese wai nembo lamaiyuo, Namba embena imwane Jetero dokome embena endape wane dolapope lanyakao epelyo, leya.
\v 7 Leyamo doko sepala Mosese papala kando nyepala pangu sepala yako lao nyinyi pyuo piya. Pipala dokopa kapa palyuo karapipi lao mendeme mende piso silya sana pipala Moseseme komau anda dokona andakare peyambi.
\v 8 Pao pisipala dokopa Isaraele wambunya reke lao Kamongo dokome Peraope dee Isipi wambu dupwape randa maiyamo doko peparae Moseseme Jetero polo lamaiya. Dee nakama kata epo randa nyiyaminyipa Kamongo dokome lete wai pyao nyiyamo dokona opetae lamaiya.
\v 9 Lamaiyamo doko sepala Jetero baa rae wakasa maiyuo dopa lao,
\v 10 Peraomoo Isipi wambu dupwape nee nyuo Kamongome emba nyisiya dokona banya kingi ketae palena. Isipi wambu dupwana kendemande yulu pyakamyuo kareyaminyipa Kamongo dokome kiiramo nyiya dokona Kamongo banya kingi ketae palena.
\v 11 Isipi wambu dupwame Isaraele wambu dupwa kando kilya kando epe kanda nayami dokopa Kamongome nyisiyamosa baame mee bange wasisi anatuŋu lao dupwa nyuo isa palyuo kamame andake wakasa karenge doko epapu soo otelyo, leya.
\v 12 Lapala Jeterome bange mende isareme kiso oto Anatu keta maiya. Dee lapo opetae kiso rendamu pingi Anatu keta maiya. Maiyamo dokopa Eronemoo Isaraele isingi akali mupwa dupwape dee Mosesena imwange dokomoo role pyao Anatunya lenge kambu dokona piso nenge neyami.
\s1 Kote Sinya Lao Akali Dupwa // Rombo Palyiya
\p 
\v 13 Dee yangama dokopa Mosese isa pisipala wambu dupwa kote leyaminyipa soo roleya. Kote siyamo dokopa wamba yangama kete pyaro karo pao yuu kwuaya.
\v 14 Kwuayamosa Moseseme pyuo kareyamo doko kandapala banya imwange Jetero dokome dopa lao piso soo, Emba doo wambu dupwa kando pilini doko akisi? Akipamo emba yeelyo pisipala wambu dupwa wamba yangama kako pyaro karo pao yuu kwuanyi reto piso soo karamisi? leya.
\p 
\v 15 Moseseme isingi lao, Anatumi mende pyakapyali lao koto namba keta epelyaminyi dokona namba kapa piru.
\v 16 Wamba lama apiyanda pipala namba keta epenge dokopa namba apinya angi rolae lao yapalyuo soo rolenge. Rolapala dokopa Anatunya mawa pii dupwa polo lamaingi, leya.
\p 
\v 17 Dokopa Jeterome Mosese lamaiyuo, Emba angi rolae pii nalene.
\v 18 Dopa pirinyi dokome embapa wambu dupwape nombe nombe piso makame kumarami. Dake yulu ama andake dokona emba iki dokome kapa yeelyo pii nara.
\v 19 Dokona epapu emba manasa keyange lapo pyarowale. Nambana pii serene dokopa Anatu baa emba role pyao karara. Kararamo dokopa Anatunya lenge kambu dokona emba wambu dupwana wai minyingi akali ingyuo karo nakama apiyaanda pirami doko Anatu keta minyuo parene doko yulu rolae.
\v 20 Embame Anatunya mawa pii dupwa mana lamaiyuo wambu dupwa apa pyuo mondo lao palyuo karapenge dee aki yulu pipenge lao polo lamairi.
\v 21 Dee yulu mende opetae piri. Akali mora petenge lapo rombo palyarene dupwame mupwa ingyuo karo wambu dupwa isarami. Isaraminyi dokopa lapome wambu taosande mendaki (1,000) iso dee lapome andete mendaki (100) iso dee lapome akalisa kingi paki (50) iso dee lapome mee akalisa mendakipi iso pirami. Nakama Anatu mupwa lao suu pyao pako karo wambumi yulu kapa pirami lao suu pyaraminde. Wambu lapome nakama kando pii elyape laraminyi dupwa yeelyo nyisa naramili lapo rombo palyape.
\v 22 Yuu peparae nakamame range kote soo wambu dupwa yapalyuo rolarami. Dopa pyuo randa andake dupwa emba keta minyuo eparami. Eparaminyipape nakama range kuki laiya lenge dupwa soo rolarami. Nakamame kukinyi pyambuo dopa piraminyi dokopa emba randa nao yulu pii nare.
\v 23 Emba Anatumi langilyamuli pyuo dopa piri ramo dokopa maka nao mona karo piri. Pirinyi dokopa wambu dupwana kote lala eparaminyi doko rolasi seramopa nakama mona yaepo anda parami, leya.
\p 
\v 24 Mosese baame Jeterona pii leyamo doko sepala leyamuli pyuo pyuo
\v 25 Isaraele akali peparaena mora petenge akali dupwa yapo rombo palyapala lapome wambu taosande mendaki (1,000) iso dee lapome andete mendaki (100) iso dee lapome akalisa kingi paki (50) iso dee lapome akalisa mendakipi iso karena leya.
\v 26 Leyamo dokopa nakama yuu peparae rangeme wambu dupwana kote pii dupwa soo rolapa piyami. Dopa pyuo randa andake dupwa Mosese keta minyuo epeyami. Epeyaminyipape kuki dupwa nakama rangeme soo rolapa piyami.
\p 
\v 27 Dokopa Moseseme banya imwange kingi nyuo pena leyamopa Jetero banya yuu range dokona kapu kyuo peya.
\c 19
\s1 Isaraele Wambu Dupwa Yuu Sainai Kyau Dokona Kareyami
\p 
\v 1 Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Isipi yaki nyiyami. Yaki nyepala kana rema yuu gii kanda soo dokona nakama yuu Orepitimi kaeyapala yuu muiyane Sainai lenge dokona epeyami.
\v 2 Epapala yuu kyau dokona isarena palyuo kareyami.
\v 3 Kareyaminyi dokopa Mosese yuu kyau dokona Anatu kando nyela peya.
\p Peyamo dokopa Kamongo dokome yuu kyau dokona karo kyakale lapala embame Jekopena para pyasi Isaraele wambu dupwa dopa lamainya leya.
\v 4 Namba Kamongo dokome Isipi wambu dupwa piyunu doko nakama kandeyami kande. Yaka kambe dokome banya ikyane papake dokona koko palyuo lanyuo penge dopale ingyuo nambame nakama lanyuo epeyo kande. Epapala nakama namba pipya role pyao karamano.
\v 5 Epapu nakama nambana pii warombo soo kana minyuo lalu lao lenge pii doko minyaro kararami ramo doko nakama namba rangena wambu ingyalu ingyuo ingyarami. Isa yuu dake peparae nambana ingyapyamopape nakama nambana rombo palyisi wambu ingyarami.
\v 6 Dopa piramopa nakama wambu namba joo otasi dokome purisi ingyuo nambana yulu pyakarami, lao Kamongome leya. Renge dusipana embame Isaraele wambu dupwa lamaipi, lao Anatumi Mosese lamaiya.
\v 7 Dokona Mosese baa isa lupyuo papala akali mupwa dupwa kee lao sukusa nyepala dokopa Kamongome pii peparae lamaiyamuli pyuo nakama polo lamaiya.
\v 8 Polo lamaiyamo dokopa wambu dupwa peparaeme isingi lao dopa leyami. Kamongo dokome lapyamo dusipa peparae kapa pirama, leyami. Leyaminyisa Moseseme dopa letaminyi lao Kamongo baa lamaiya.
\p 
\v 9 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo, Namba kopa romende rakapana piso emba keta eparo. Epapala wambu dupwa kapa serami lao emba pii langiru. Renge dokona lao wambu dupwame yuu peparae kinyi lapilyamo lao soo nyerami, leya.
\p Leyamo dokopa wambu dupwana pii isingi leyaminyi doko Moseseme Kamongo baa lamaiya.
\v 10 Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo, Wambu petaminyi suku dokona pao nambana kingi ketae pyambuo lakandarami dokona epapu rakyapana nakamana koo dupwa polo lao rapa rapa pinya lamairi. Nakamana komau dupwa wate pipala
\v 11 jimwa dokopa nakama rapa rapa pisi kararami. Yuu gii dokopa namba yuu kyau manda Sainai lenge dokona eparonopa wambu peparaeme namba kandarami.
\v 12 Wambu dupwa yalo epa nana lapala yuu kyau dokona repeta rombo palyuo liti pipala dopa lamaiyuo, Nakama yuu kyau dokona pulyuo paope repeta paope pii nana lamairi. Daaŋa lapala mendeme dokona kimbu palyuo para ramo doko kumara.
\v 13 Dopa piramo dokopa mendemepe baa minyandapa naramopa wanga kanapeme pyarami. Pii dake mena wambupi peparae keta epelyamo. Nakama peparae kumarami. Dopa piraminyipape bikuli pii laramo dokopa wambu dupwa yuu kyau dokona pulyuo parami, leya.
\p 
\v 14 Dokopa Mosese yuu kyau dokona karo wambu peteyaminyi dokona epapala Kamongo kingi ketae pyambuo lakandarami lao rapa rapa pinya leya. Dokona nakamana komau dupwa wate piyami.
\v 15 Piyaminyi dokopa Mosese nakama lamaiyuo, Jimwa yuu gii dokopa nakama rapa rapa pisi kararami. Dokona epapu rakyapana enda akalipa nyingi dolapo role pyao pali nalapape, leya. \fig Anatumi yuu gala role pyapeta banya pii isingi leya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="19:19"\fig*
\p 
\v 16 Yuu gii repo dokopa yangama yuu kyau dokona yuu gala lao yuu pele pyuo dee kopa andake soo pipala bikuli pii andake leya. Leyamo dokopa wambu palyuo kareyaminyi dupwa sepala walu lao pakame kumuyami.
\v 17 Moseseme wambu palyuo kareyaminyi dokona yaki neypala Anatu kando nyinya lao laminyuo peya. Nakama pao yuu kyau dokona isarena kareyami.
\v 18 Kareyaminyi dokopa Kamongo doko isare piso yuu kyau manda Sainai dokona epeyamosa yuu kyau doko sukwa dokome yambe pyao oteya. Poo kisilyaminyipa isare sukwa pulyuo penge dopale ingyuo sukwa doko pulyuo peya. Peyamo dokopa wambu dupwa peparae pakame kumuo walu walu lao kareyami.
\v 19 Bikuli pii andake lao ama ketae palyuo uliuli leyamo dokopa Moseseme pii leyamopa Anatumi yuu gala role pyapeta banya pii isingi leya.
\v 20 Lapala Kamongo doko yuu kyau manda Sainai dokona isa epapala baame Mosese yuu kyau dokona pulyuo epena lao kee leya. Kee leyamo dokopa Mosese baa yuu kyau dokona pulyuo peya.
\v 21 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo, Emba lupyuo papala wambu dupwame namba kandarama lao yuu liti doko yalo epa nana lao repe repe pii lamairi. Doko kaepala eparami ramo doko wambu malu kumarami.
\v 22 Dee purisi akali namba repeta epo kararaminyi dupwa nakama poo pyasi ingyuo kararami. Poo pyasi ingyuo kara naraminyi dupwa nambame nakama randa mairu, leya.
\p 
\v 23 Moseseme Kamongo doko lamaiyuo, Emba namwa kando repe repe lao yuu kyau doko liti pyuo poo pyasi ingyuo sinyale lao langyuo otee kande dokona wambu dupwa pulyuo epa narami, leya.
\p 
\v 24 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Mosese isingi lamaiyuo, Emba isa lupyuo papala dokopa Erone nyuo minyuo kapu kyuo ipupi. Eparene dokopa purisi akali dupwape mee wambu dupwape yuu liti doko yalapala namba kandala epa narami. Eparami ramo doko nakama nambame randa mairu, leya.
\v 25 Leyamo dokopa Mosese baa wambu peteyaminyi dokona isa lupyuo papala nakama Kamongome leyamuli pyuo lamaiya.
\c 20
\s1 Mawa Pii Akalisa Dusipa
\p 
\v 1 Pii dasipa peparae Anatu baame leya.
\v 2 Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome nakama yuu Isipi dokona karapusi ingyuo kendemande yulu pyuo kareyaminyipa neta nyuo lanyuo epeyoŋo doko.
\p 
\v 3 Nakambame namba iki lakando anatu wakale mende lakanda nalapape.
\p 
\v 4 Nakamame yake ketae bange singipi panda isa yuunya singipi panda ipwa isarena yuu koko palenge dokona singipi dupwana yale mendeme anatuŋu lao wasa nalapape.
\v 5 Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatu. Wakale mendeme nambana panda nyinya lao maiya nange. Dokona lao mee bange anatu angi daa dupwana ponga napala kingi ketae pyambuo lakanda nalapape. Wambu mendeme namba awa nara ramo dokopa nakamana para pyaraminyi dupwame manjo jingi para pyao paraminyipa rema panda kisima ingyuo manjiraminyi dusipana mende keta randa mairu.
\v 6 Dopa pirunupape wambu malu mee namba mona retapala nambana mawa pii dusipa minyaro kararaminyi dupwa nambame mona retalu reto retenge.
\p 
\v 7 Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome nambana kingi dokona kopetame koo ingyuo laraminyi dupwa randa mairu dokona nakamame nambana kingi doko kopetame ingyuo kwuanyi nembo laa nalapape.
\p 
\v 8 Koro petenge yuu gii dokona lao poraiyuo suu pyao minyaro karo yapasi ingyuo Kamongo keta pyambwarami.
\v 9 Pyambwapala yuu gii pakinyamange dusipana nakamana yulu dupwa kapa pirami ingilyamo.
\v 10 Pipala yuu gii yanda ipingi nyepo dokona imambu soo karo nakamana Kamongo Anatu lao poraiyuo suu pyao kararami. Yuu gii dokopa nakamape nakamana wane wanakepe nakamana kendemande yulu pyakange akalipi menape yuu nanesa range nakamana yuu dokona karengepe peparae yulu pii narami.
\v 11 Yuu gii pakinyamange dusipana namba Kamongo dokome yakepe yuupi ipwa kotape dee dusipana bange peparae singipi dupwa wasiyu. Wasiyunupape yuu gii yanda ipingi dokona namba imambu soo peteyo. Renge dokona namba Kamongo dokome koro petenge yuu gii doko mupwa lao yapasi ingyuo sinya lao reteyo.
\p 
\v 12 Endangi rakangepa kando rape rape lao karalapape. Nambame nakama yuu jilyu dokona yuu gii londesa palyuo kararama lao dopa pirami.
\p 
\v 13 Wambu pyao kumaka nalapape.
\p 
\v 14 Endame akali wakale kepo pyakami nao akali mendeme enda wakale kepo pyakami nao pipwape.
\p 
\v 15 Waa nyakami nalapape.
\p 
\v 16 Nakamame wambu yango mende kando koo pipya lamo lao panga soo kyambo lakami nalapape.
\p 
\v 17 Akali mendena anda awuapala nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pyaa nalapape. Banya etengepe kendemande akalipi mena bulamakaope mena dongepe dee banya bange wakale wakale silyamo dupwana mendepe nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pyaa nalapape.
\s1 Wambu Dupwa Pakame Kumuyami
\p 
\v 18 Wambu dupwa yuu gala lao bikuli pii andake lao piyamo doko soo dee yuu kyau dokona yuu pele lao sukwa dokome yambe piyamo doko kando pipala walu lao pakame kumapala nanesa wakale kareyami.
\v 19 Karapala nakamame Mosese lamaiyuo, Embame namwa pii langirinyi dokopa namwa pii serama. Dopa piramopape Anatumi namwa pii langira ramo dokopa namwa kumaseramano lao pakame kumulyamano, leyami.
\p 
\v 20 Leyaminyi dokopa Moseseme wambu dupwa isingi lamaiyuo, Paka nalapape. Nakama yuu peparae Anatu baa mupwa lao suu pyao pakame kumuo karapala yulu koo dokona pii narami lao baame nakama makande pilyamo, leya.
\v 21 Dopa leyamopape wambu dupwa nanesako karo peyaminyipa kopa soo iminjo koro koro leyamo Anatu baa kareyamo dokona Mosese baa iki repeta peya.
\s3 20:22—23:33 Lowa piipi mana piipi lapo pyasi palamo dapwa. Wambu dupwa keta anjiki pyuo yulu rolae piyamipi dee wambu koo wakale wakale piyami dupwana randa maiyamipi dee apa pyuo yuu doko au pyuo iso kareyami laope dee apa pyuo misi laope nenge nenge yuu gii andake dusipana yulu piyamipi lao pii dupwa pyasi palamo. Wambu mendeme banya yangona yuupi andape kokwa siyaminyipa aki bange mende isingi maiyami pii doko opetaeko palamo.
\c 24
\s1 Kana Minyuo Kinyi Lalu Lao Lenge Doko Angiŋi Lao Lasaka Piya
\p 
\v 1 Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Embamoo Erone Natapi Apiyumoo dee Isaraele wambunya akali mupwa akalisa yanda ipingi nyepo dusipa pipya yuu kyau namba karo dokona pulyuo ipupwape. Epapala nakama mee mende nanesale epo karo dokopa wapambu pii pyaro piso nambana kingi ketae pyambuo lakandarami.
\v 2 Dopa pipala emba iki namba repeta eparenepa akali mupwa dupwana mende namba repeta epa narami. Dee wambu dupwana mendepe kamame yuu kyau dokona pulyuo epa naramiko, leya.
\p 
\v 3 Leyamo dokopa Mosese baa wambu peteyaminyi sukusa dokona papala Kamongona mawa pii leyamo dupwa peparaepe banya mana piipi lamaiya. Lamaiyamo dokopa wambu peparaeme kapa kapa isingi lao, Kapa namwame Kamongo dokome lapyamuli pyuo peparae pirama, leyami.
\v 4 Dokopa Moseseme Kamongona mawa pii dusipa peparae pepana pyao reteya. Retapala yuu gii mende dokona wamba yangama baame yuu kyau isarena dokona kana pyare lao mena kiso maingi rate piya. Pipala kana akalisa ipisu lama malu palyuo pyuo reteya. Reteyamo dusipa Isaraele rara akalisa ipisu lamako dusipana kana mendaki mendaki lao retakamiya.
\v 5 Dopa pipala dokopa baame akali parange lapo pena leyamopa papala nakamame mena pyao isareme kiso mukinyi nembo Kamongo maiyuo dee Anatupa wambupi mona mendaki palyuo mena bulamakao lapo pyao kiso maiyuo piyami.
\v 6 Moseseme mena ranjama dokona lapo pingyu kamuo nyuo pere warake dupwana reteya. Retapala ranjama pingyasi siyamo doko kamuo nyuo kana pyare lasi dokona pyarenda lanyi pisiya.
\v 7 Dopa pipala enakana kana minyuo lalu lao lenge pii palenge buku dokona Kamongona mawa pii pyasi palenge doko baame nyiya. Nyepala pii ketae palyuo wambu dupwa yaka lao lamaiya. Lamaiyamo dokopa wambu dupwame lao, Namwame Kamongo warombo soo baame pelapa lao mawa pii langilyamuli pyuo yulu peparae pirama, leyami.
\p 
\v 8 Enakana Moseseme ranjama pere dupwana siyamo doko nyepala wambu dupwa keta pyarenda lanyi pisiya. Pisapala baame dopa leya. Mawa pii peparae joo karo dokopa Kamongo dokome nakama pipya kana minyuo lalu lao leyamo pii dupwa ranjama dakeme kiso pii kapa wai wara pisi silyamo, leya.
\p 
\v 9 Mosesemoo Erone Natapi Apiyumoo dee Isaraele wambunya akali kyawa akalisa yanda ipingi nyepo dusipa pipya yuu kyau dokona pulyuo peyami.
\v 10 Papala Isaraele wambunya Anatu doko angi kandeyami. Kandeyaminyi dokopa banya kimbu siyamo dokona isarena kata kana kameya mende sapaiya lenge dokome wasisi siya. Kana doko kala ama muku wakasa yake dopale ingyuo siya.
\v 11 Isaraele akali mupwa dusipame Anatu kandeyaminyipape baame nakama randa maiyuo pyaa naya. Enakana nakama pyaso piso nenge ipwape neyami.
\s1 Mosese Baa Yuu Kyau Sainai // Dokona Kareya
\p 
\v 12 Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo, Emba yuu kyau namba karo dakena ipupi. Epo kararene dokopa wambu dupwa lowa peparae kapa mana nyerami lao kana para lamana pyao reteyono dolapo jero.
\v 13 Mosesepa banya nyisingi Josuapa rapa rapa pyuo oteyambinyipa Mosese baa yuu kyau poo pyasi dokona kanda soo pulyuo peya.
\v 14 Moseseme akali mupwa dupwa lamaiyuo, Namba kamba kapu kyuo epelyambipi lao isaro karalapape. Eronepa Uapa nakama pipya role pyao karaminyi. Dokona nakama mendali randa mende paleya kande dokopa akali dolapome lao rolakarambiŋi nakamba keta maiyuo pupwape, leya.
\p 
\v 15 Mosese baa yuu kyau Sainai dokona pulyuo peyamo dokopa kopa dokome yambe piya.
\v 16-17 Kamongona lepo lepo pyuo yanga paupau lenge doko yuu Sainai kyau dokona isa epeya. Epeyamo doko Isaraele wambu dupwame Kamongona yanga paupau lenge doko isare dopale ingyuo yuu kyau dokona rao kareyamo kandeyami. Dokopa yuu gii pakinyamange kopa dokome yuu kyau doko yambe pyaro karalu kareya. Kareyamopa yuu gii yanda ipingi nyepo dokona kopa rakapana sukusa Kamongo dokome Mosese lao kee leya.
\v 18 Kee leyamo dokopa Mosese baa kopa rakapana sukusa dokona pao yuu kyau dokona pulyuo peya. Papala baa yuu kyau dokona yuu gii akalisa kisima dee kukwama akalisa kisimako kareya.
\s3 25:1—31:17 Anatu baame Mosese pii lapo lamaiya. Apa pyuo baame komaumi wasisi misi andape pyuo dee bange wakale wakale andakare retengepe dupwa peparae wasara lao Antumi polo lamaiya. Dee kana bangepe wambu dupwame Anatu mairami dupwana leyamo pii pyasi palamoko.
\c 31
\p 
\v 18 Yuu Sainai kyau dokona Kamongome Mosese pii lamaiyuo otapala kana para dolapona baa rangeme mawa pii dupwa pyao palyapala maiya.
\c 32
\s1 Bulamakao Ikyane Golome Wasisi Doko
\p 
\v 1 Mosese baa isa epa nao yuu kyau dokona andarele kareyamopa wambu dupwame kandapala Erone kareyamo dokona sukusa sukusa pyuo epapala dopa lamaiyuo, Namwa Isipi kareyamanopa nyuo lanyuo epeyamo akali Mosese doko epapu apa pilyamo lao soo gisa nalyamano. Dokona mee bange anatu lao mende wasakape. Dokome namwa lanyuo penale, leyami.
\p 
\v 2 Dokopa Eroneme nakama lamaiyuo, Nakamana endape wanepe wanakepe dupwana kana golome kalena pingi bange dupwa nyepala namba karo dakena minyuo ipupwape, leya.
\v 3 Dokopa wambu peparaeme kana golome kalena pingi bange dupwa nyisa nyepala minyuo epo Erone maiyami.
\v 4 Dokopa baame kana golo kalena pingi dupwa nyepala kiso lili lao ipwa ingiya. Ingiyamopa yuwale mena bulamakao dopale ingyuo apu rao reteyaminyi dokona golo ipwange doko kulimbwanyi pyambuya. Pyambuyamopa golo dokome bulamakao ikyane wasiya.
\p Dokopa wambu dupwame lao, Isaraele dupwa dake namwana anatu yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo epeyamo dokoŋo, leyami.
\p 
\v 5 Dokopa Eroneme golome wasisi mena bulamakao kareyamo lenge kambu dokona kana pyare mende leya. Lapala lao, Rakya Kamongo doko kingi ketae pyambuo lakando nenge andake kiso mairama, leya.
\v 6 Leyamo dokopa yuu gii mende dokona wamba yangama dokopa wambu dupwame mena lapo minyuo epo pyao kiso maiyuo dee lapo dupwa nakama pipya Anatumoo mona mendaki palyuo kiso maiyuo piyami. Pipala nakama nenge nao piso kopetame pyuo ipwa biya nao kepo pyuo peteyami.
\p 
\v 7 Dopa piyaminyisa Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Embena wambu yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo epee kande dupwame namba mata joo yulu koo pilyaminyi dokona dakepa aopa waiya lao lupyuo puu, leya.
\v 8 Dopa lao, Nambame nakama mawa pii lamaipala moko minyuo pinya leyono doko yaki nyuo otami. Dopa pipala nakama kana golo kiso lili lapala mena bulamakao mende wasami. Wasapala doko lakando mena pyao kiso maimi. Maipala nakamame lao, Dake namwana anatu namwa yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo epeyamo dokoŋo, lami.
\v 9 Nakamana mona kana poko pilyaminyi doko namba silyu, leya.
\v 10 Namba nakama pipya imbuo pyao kokwa sero dokona epapu embame namba daa lao kata rokwa napipi. Dopa pirunu dokopa embape embena para pyarene dupwape jingi para pyao andakinyi pyambwaro, leya Kamongome.
\p 
\v 11 Leyamopape Moseseme banya Kamongo Anatu doko kando poraiyuo piso sokondali pyuo lao, Kamongo embame embena wambu dupwa kyawa lete nyuo yuu Isipi piso embena porainya renge dokome nyuo minyuo epee dupwa akipamo nakama kando imbumi kumarese?
\v 12 Isipi wambu dupwame dopa lao, Embena wambu yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo pee dupwa yuu kyau dokona pyao kumuo kokwa soo nembalu nembo nembalana lanyuo pee lyamo lao akipamo laramisi? Dokona imbwa nao embena suu pingi alowa pipala embena wambu dupwa keta randa doko mai napipi.
\v 13 Embena kendemande akali Aporakame Aisake Jekopemoo dusipana lao suu pyaro karape. Karo nakama kando embena pii lalu lao lao, Nakamana wane manjiraminyi dupwa kamame wakasa yakena bui dopale ingyuo ando kararami. Nakamana para pyaraminyi dupwame yuu mairu lalu lao leene doko nakamana ingyuo dokona palyuo karalu kararami leene doko suu pyaro karape, leya.
\v 14 Leyamosa Kamongo dokome banya wambu dupwa randa maiyuo pyalana suu piyamo doko alowa pipala pyaa naya.
\p 
\v 15 Dokopa Mosese yuu kyau doko yaki nyuo kana para lamana paki pakipi mawa pii dupwa pyasi paleyamo dolapo soo lupyuo peya.
\v 16 Anatumi baa rangme kana para lama wasapala dolapona mawa pii peparae pyao reteya.
\p 
\v 17 Wambu dupwame pii porakai leyaminyi doko Josuame sepala Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Wambu dupwa paliminyi yuu dokona yanda pyuo pii laminyi doko silyu, leya.
\p 
\v 18 Leyamo dokopa Moseseme lao, Doo letaminyi dokome yanda pyuo wini pipala letaminyi ingya naope panda pyao anamasi minya napala ee lenge dopale ingya naope pilyamo. Doko mee kenane poponge epelyamo, leya.
\p 
\v 19 Lapala Mosese baa yuu paleyaminyi dokona repetale epo karo mena bulamakao dokope wambu rae maiyuo kenane pyao malya pyao kareyaminyi dupwape kandeya. Kandapala baa ama imbumi kumapala kana lama soo epeyamo dolapo yuu kyau dokona isarena pyao pisiyasa poro leya.
\v 20 Dopa pipala baame mena bulamakao wasiyaminyi doko nyepala isarena kiso kuku piya. Pipala kuku pisi dupwa nyuo ipwa dokona pyasiya. Pyasapala Isaraele wambu dupwa kamuo nena leya.
\v 21 Dokopa Moseseme Erone kando lao, Wambu dupwame emba kando aki koo mende pimisa embame nakama yulu koo andake dake kapa pinya lao panda maipisi? leya.
\p 
\v 22 Dokopa Eroneme isingi lao, Embame namba kando imbwa napipi. Wambu dapwa rangeme porayapala yulu koo doko pimwalinya suu pyao karenge doko emba soo otelene.
\v 23 Wambu dupwa dopa lanyuo, Mosese Isipi karo namwa nyuo lanyuo epeya doko epapu baa apa pilyape lao see nalyamano dokona epapu embame anatu mende namwa lanyuo para lao wasakape, leyami.
\v 24 Dopa leyaminyi dokopa kana golome wasisi kalya pingi bange dupwa minyuo epo jinya leyo. Dokopa wambu lapome bange reteyaminyi dupwa nyisa nyepala jiyami. Jiyaminyi dupwa isare dokona pyao pyambuyu dokopa bulamakao ikyane dake mee maso sipuro epeya, leya.
\p 
\v 25 Erone baame Isaraele wambu dupwa poraiyuo rapu pii nayamosa mee bolombalo lao karo yulu kopetame pyuo kareyaminyipa yanda pimwai dupwame nakama kando giyuo kareyami. Dopa piyaminyi doko Mosese kandeya.
\v 26 Kandapala Mosese baa yuu paleyaminyi kame kambu doko karapala poraiyuo kyakale lao, Nakama lapo Kamongona wambu ingyuo karaminyi dupwa namba karo dakena ipupwape, leya. Leyamo dokopa Lipae wambu peparae dupwa baa kareyamo dokona epo malu palyiyami.
\v 27 Baame nakama lamaiyuo lao, Kamongo Isaraele wambunya Anatu dokome nakama peparae langyuo, Mendaki mendaki lao embena wua gela doko nyuo minyapala yuu palaminyi dokona kanda kanda kame kambu dakena piso pao paki oto embena yangonepe puu minyingipi dee parali maki palengepe dupwa pyao kumakalapape letamo, leya.
\v 28 Leyamo yuu gii dokopako Lipae akali dupwame warombo sepala wambu ama malu taosande rema (3,000) pyao kumuyami.
\v 29 Dokopa Moseseme Lipae akali dupwa lamaiyuo lao, Nakamana yangongepe ikinyingipi dupwa pyao kumakami dokona nakama yapasi ingyuo Kamongona purisi karaminyi. Dokona Kamongo dokome nakama elyape keta pisapya, leya.
\p 
\v 30 Yuu gii yangama dokopa Moseseme wambu dupwa lamaiyuo, Nakamame yulu koo dae pimi dake kamame koo ingyuo pelyamo. Dokona epapu namba yuu kyau Kamongo karamo doko dee kamba paro. Papala nambame nakamana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakana lao piso sero dokopa baame kame sakara rapisi, leya.
\v 31 Lapala Mosese kamba kapu kyuo pulyuo papala Kamongo doko lamaiyuo, Wambu dupwame yulu koo andake pyuo kana golome anatu wakale wasapala doko lakando karami.
\v 32 Dokona nakamana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakamipi. Kame sakami nare ramo doko buku embena wambu dupwa kingi pyao palyingi dokona nambana kingi palamo doko kwuanyi nembakape, leya.
\p 
\v 33 Leyamo dokopa Kamongo dokome isingi lao, Doko wambu namba kando koo piminyi dupwana kingi dupwa nambana buku dokona pali nana lao kwuanyi nembaro, leya.
\v 34 Dokona epapu nambame emba langiyunu yuu dokona wambu dupwa lanyuo pupi. Parene dokopa nambana aŋala dokome emba rapu pyuo karara. Dopa piramopape wambu dupwa koo piyami dokona randa mairunu yuu gii doko pyaka sera, leya.
\p 
\v 35 Wambu dupwame Erone kando mena bulamakao ikyane golome wasakana leyaminyi dokona Kamongo dokome anga ikyane mende wambu keta peeya.
\c 33
\s1 Yuu Kyau Sainai Doko Yaki Nyinya // Lao Lamaiya
\p 
\v 1 Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Embape embena wambu yuu Isipi yaki nyuo lanyuo epee dupwape yuu dake yaki nyepala nambame Aporakame Aisake Jekopemoope dee dupwana para pyaraminyi dupwape kando yuu mairuŋu lao lalu lao leyono dokona pupwape.
\v 2 Nambame aŋala mende nakama rapu pinya lao mapanyi peeyapala nambame Kenane rangepe Amo rangepe Ipi rangepe Perasi rangepe Iti rangepe dee Jepusi rangepe peparae ralinyi nembaro.
\v 3 Dokopa nakama yuu keyange amenge kapape pingi dokona parami. Dopa pyuo paraminyipape nakama waiya lao mona kana pokonge dokona nambame katasa nakama pyao kokwa soo nembasaroŋo namba range role pyao paa narama, leya.
\p 
\v 4 Wambu dupwame pii porai doko sepala nakama kondome kumuo ee lao mona kendo karo nakamana kalya pingi bange dupwa dee nyuo pirami ingya nayami.
\v 5 Dopa piyaminyi dokopa Kamongome Mosese kando wambu dupwa lamainya lao lao, Nakama wambu mona kana pokonge dapwa namba nakama role pyao mee kuki lama pao lapuli doko nambame nakama pyao kokwa soo nembalu nembo nembapuli. Namba nakama keta aki mende piru lao suu pyarole. Epapu nakamana kalya pingi bange dupwa kako lao nyisa nyelapape, leya.
\v 6 Leyamo dokona lao nakama yuu kyau Sainai yaki nyuo papeyaminyi dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwa kalya pingi bange dupwa pyuo kara nayami.
\s1 Kamongona Komau Anda Doko
\p 
\v 7 Yuu dupwana mendepe Isaraele wambu komau anda dupwa pyuo palenge dokopa Mosese baame komau anda poo pyasi doko nyepala yuu palenge dokona mee mende nanesale ingyuo piya. Pipala doko komau anda dokona Kamongo karenge doko leyami. Dokopa wambu lapo Anatu pii mende piso selana masiyami dupwa dokona pao pii lamaiyami.
\v 8 Yuu gii lapo Mosese komau anda dokona panya peyamo dokopa wambu dupwa peparae nakamana komau anda kambu dokona kando karo pao konandeyamo dokopa kaeyami.
\v 9 Enakana Mosese baa andakare pao oteyamo dokopa kopa rau doko epo komau anda kambu dowa dokona siya. Dokopa kopa rakapana piso Kamongome Mosese pii lamaiya.
\v 10 Dokopa wambu dupwame kopa rau komau anda kambu dokona epo siyamo doko kandapala aopa wapambu pii pyaro pangu soo Anatu lakandeyami.
\v 11 Doko wambu puu minyingi dupwa rolae lenge kambu kando pii lenge dokoko suu pyao Kamongome Mosese role pyao karo lenge kambu kando pii lamaiya. Lamaipala Mosese baa wambu dupwa palenge yuu dokona peya. Dopa pyuo peyamopape banya nyisingi wane parange akali Nanena ikinyingi Josua lenge doko komau anda dokona yaki nyii nao mee andakare kareya.
\s1 Kamongo Dokome Banya Wambu Dupwa Pipya Role Kararo lao Pii Lalu Lao Leya
\p 
\v 12 Dokopa Mosese Kamongo doko lamaiyuo lao, Doko kinyi. Emba namba langyuo, Wambu dapwa minyuo yuu dokona puu lee. Leenepape embame wambu mende nambapa role parambi peeyaro lao namba langi nae. Embame lao, Namba emba soo oto rae mailyu, lee.
\v 13 Epapu embame namba kando rae mairi ramo doko embena rapa rapa piinyi dupwa namba langipi. Dokona nambame embena yulu pyakao emba rae maiyuo puu paro. Dee wambu rara dake emba rangena ingyara lao rombo palyinyi doko suu pyao karape, leya.
\p 
\v 14 Leyamo dokopa Kamongo dokome lao, Namba nakama role paramanopa nakamame anamasi minyuo wini pirami, leya.
\p 
\v 15 Dokopa Moseseme isingi lao, Emba namwa role pyao paa narama ramo doko namwa yuu dake yaki nyelapa lao laa napipi.
\v 16 Emba namwa pipya paa narama ramo doko embame embena wambupi nambape kando rae mailiŋi lao apa pyuo wambu mendeme soo nyerase? Emba namwa pipya role parama ramo doko wambu dupwame namwa rara wakaleŋe lao soo nyerami, leya.
\p 
\v 17 Dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Nambame emba soo giso rae maiyuo pilyu dokona embame piso silinyili pyuo piru, leya.
\p 
\v 18 Dokopa Moseseme piso soo lao, Embena yanga paupau lao lepo lepo pingi doko namba lasaka pii, leya.
\p 
\v 19 Kamongo dokome isingi lao, Nambame nambana yanga paupau lenge peparae emba lasaka pyuo embena lenge kambu dokona nambana kingi poo pyasi doko polo langiru. Namba Kamongo doko. Namba rangeme mendali sakame kumuo kondo nyiso kararo laro ramo doko sakame kumuo kondo nyiso kararo.
\v 20 Mendeme namba kandapala lete paa nange dokona emba nambana lenge kambu doko kanda laa naro.
\v 21 Dopa piramopape emba kanana ketae karare lao namba karo dakena paki panda mende silyamo.
\v 22 Nambana yanga paupau lao lepo lepo pingi doko embena lenge kambu dokona eparamo dokopa nambame kana dokona kata silyamo koko dokona emba palyapala nambana kingi dokome emba yambe pyaro. Yambe pyapala namba pao otaro.
\v 23 Pao otapala enakana nambana kingi neta nyero dokopa embame nambana matarena yeelyo kandare. Nambana lenge kamburena kanda nare, leya.
\c 34
\s1 Kana Para Lama Dee Kamba Maiya
\r (Du 10:1-5)
\p 
\v 1 Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Kana wambo dopale ingyuo embame kana lama kunjo wasape. Wasarene dokopa kana wambo embame pyao poro leene dolapona pii paleyamo dupwa nambame dee kamba pyao retaro.
\v 2 Rakya yangama rapa rapa pipala yuu kyau Sainai dokona epo ketae nambapa role pyao kararamba.
\v 3 Wambu mende role pyao epa nara. Dee yuu kyau dupwana mendasape wambu mende kara narami. Mena sipisipipi panda mena bulamakaope dupwame yuu kyau wangu kipwa kipwa isako nao pii nana, leya.
\v 4 Dokona lao Moseseme kana lama kamba kunjo wasiya. Wasapala Kamongome lamaiyamuli pyuo wamba yangama dokopa yuu kyau Sainai dokona soo pulyuo peya.
\p 
\v 5 Dokopa Kamongo baa kopa rakapana isa epo dokona baapa role kareya. Karo dokopa banya kingi poo pyasi Kamongo doko leya.
\v 6 Dokopa Kamongome Mosesena lenge kambusa papala kee lao lao, Namba Kamongo doko Anatu kondome kumuo nyiso karenge. Dopa pyuo karo dokopa namba waiya lao imbwa nange. Dee namba yaki nyii nao mona retenge renge andake doko nakama keta palyingi.
\v 7 Nambame nakamana para pyasi dupwana mendeme mende manjipa pyuo penge ama malu soo kaeyo dupwa keta lalu lao leyonde pyuo pyuo koo pingi peparae kame sakamyuo karenge. Dopa pirunupape endangi rakangepe koo piraminyi dokona palyuo nambame nakamana ikinyingi wanengepe apusingipi kauwangepe dee dupwana para pyasi wambu rara lama manjiraminyi dupwape randa malisa nao mairu.
\p 
\v 8 Mosese baa waiya lao yuu dokona wapambu pii pyaro piso Anatu lakandeya.
\v 9 Lakando baame lao, Kamongo embame namba kando angi rae mairi ramo doko namwa pipya emba role pyao mona ipu lao piso silyu. Wambu dapwa mona kana pokolyaminyipape embame namwana koo peparae nyuo kame sakapala namwa emba rangena wambu ingyuo manjo nyepe, leya.
\s1 Anatumi Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Doko Kambako lao Pyao Reteya
\r (Du 7:1-5)
\p 
\v 10 Leyamo dokopa Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo lao, Epapu nambame Isaraele wambu dupwa keta kana minyuo lalu lao lenge pii doko retelyo. Nambame yuu muu dakenape mendasa wambu rara palaminyi dupwa ketape yulu pii nangende Isaraele wambunya lenge kambu dokona piru. Nambame yulu mende wambu kando yamarangyuo kararaminyi doko nakamana lao pyakaro dokona wambu peparaeme namba Kamongo dokome aki yulu andake lapo pilini lao kandarami.
\v 11 Nambame nakama epapu mawa pii jilyu dupwa warombo soo karalapape. Nakama paraminyi dokona nambame wambo pao Amo rangepe Kenane rangepe Iti rangepe Perasi rangepe Ipi rangepe dee Jepusi rangepe peparae neta pyao ralinyi nembaro.
\v 12 Kando pupwape. Papala nakama yuu dokona range wambu dupwa pipya pelyaminyi pii lalu lao laa nalapape. Dopa pirami ramo nakama randa nyuo koo keta pao konena lyakaro karele lasarami.
\v 13 Dopa pyuo kara nao nakamana nenge kiso maingi kana pyare dupwa lalyuo nembalapape. Nakamana isa pote poo pyasi lenge dupwa pyao lalyalapape. Lalyapala dee nakamana isa lapo kando Asera enda anatu lenge doko pyakepo muu muu pinyi nembo pipwape.
\p 
\v 14 Nakamame anatu wakale lapo lakanda nalapape. Namba Kamongo dokome nambana wambu dupwa yulu kopetame dopale dupwa pinya lao yaki nyii nao nakama nambana iki ingyuo karamili yaka lao suu pilyu.
\v 15 Doko wambu dupwame mee bange anatu lenge doko mena pyao kiso mainya lao nakama dokona role pyao yalya kando pisala ipupwa lao piso seraminyi dokopa wambu dupwana anatu nenge kisaraminyi doko walu lapala nyuo nasaramiŋi dokona yuu range wambu dupwa kando pii lalu lao laa nalapape.
\p 
\v 16 Dokona nakamana ikinyingi dupwame yuu wakale range enda dupwa nyerami ramo enda dupwame nakama kata koo dokona lanyuo paraminyisa nakamame namba angi suu pyaa napala mee bange anatu kyambo lenge dupwa lakandarami ingilyamo.
\p 
\v 17 Nakamame kana golope kulingipi dupwame mee bange anatu lao wasapala lakanda nalapape.
\p 
\v 18 Nakama Borete Isi Pyambwa Nange Nenge Nenge yuu gii doko minyuo karalapape. Karapala nambame langiyunuli pyuo nakama borete isi pyambwa nange doko kana Apipi dokona yuu yanda ipingi dusipana narami. Kana Apipi dokona nakama yuu Isipi yaki nyuo epeyaminyi dokona ingyuo narami.
\p 
\v 19 Nakamana wane ane mupwa manjiraminyi peparaepe bulamakao kali mupwape mena sipisipipinya kali mupwape manjiraminyi dupwa peparae nambana ingyara.
\v 20 Dopa piramopape nakamame mena donge wambo mandenge dupwa ropo pyao nyuo mena sipisipi ikyane dupwa panda nyuo kiso jerami. Dopa pyuo kiso jii narami ramo doko dongena mange dupwa minyuo roo pyarami. Dopa pipala nakamana wane wambo mandenge dupwa ropo pyao range nyerami. Dokona mendeme nenge kiso jii napala mee nambana arapu dokona epo maro laa narami.
\p 
\v 21 Dokona nakamame yulu pirami lao yuu gii pakinyamange silyamo. Sipyamopa yuu gii yanda ipingi dokona yulu pii nalapape. Dee yuu ape ape pingi dokopape witi jingi lyingi dokopape yuu gii yanda ipingi dokona kamame pii narami.
\p 
\v 22 Nakamame witi jingi kanda soo mupwa lyuo nyeraminyi dokopa wambu nenge nao nyuo malu palyingi doko yaki nyii nao minyaro karalapape. Karapala nakamana isa jingi poo relyamo lyuo anda kauwa dokona piso nenge nenge yuu gii doko minyuo karo pipwape.
\p 
\v 23 Ee kana yaka lao yuu gii rema larapu nakamana akali dupwa peparaeme namba Kamongo doo Isaraele wambunya Anatu lakandarapu pinya.
\v 24 Nambame nakamana lenge kambu dokona wambu rara dupwa pyao ralinyi nembaparono dokopa nakamana yuu doko konda pyuo andake ingyakaro. Dokopa nakama nenge nyuo malu palyuo naraminyi yuu gii rema dusipana mendemepe nakamana yuu doko nyuo isa palyuo anamasi minya narami ingilyamo.
\p 
\v 25 Namba mena pyao kiso jeraminyi dokopa nakamame borete isi pyambwange doko role pyao kisa nalapape. Dee Pasopa Nenge Nenge yuu gii dokona mena pyao kisaraminyi dokona mena injisipi rakya yangamana lao mende reta nalapape.
\p 
\v 26 Dokona ee kana yaka lao witi jingi mupwa kanda soo lyeraminyi dupwa Kamongona anda dokona minyuo ipupwape. Dee mena sipisipi ikyanepe mena meme ikyanepe kisaraminyi dupwa endanginya anju ipwange kamuo nyepala pyambuo kisa nalapape, leya.
\p 
\v 27 Lapala Kamongo dokome Mosese lamaiyuo, Pii dasipame nambame embape Isaraele wambupi pipya kana minyuo lalu lao leto dokoŋo pyao retape, leya.
\v 28 Dokopa kukwa yuu gii akalisa kisimako korakama yuu gii akalisa kisimako dusipana Mosese baa nenge ipwape naa nao Anatupa role pyao kareyambi. Dokopa baame pii kana minyuo lalu lao lenge mawa pii akalisa dusipa kana para dolapona pyao reteya.
\s1 Mosese Baa Yuu Kyau Sainai Dokona Karo Lupyuo Peya
\p 
\v 29 Mosese baa yuu kyau Sainai dokona karo mawa pii akalisa pyasi palenge kana para lama soo lupyuo peya. Peyamo dokopa baa Kamongopa pii lao kareyambinyi dokome banya lenge kambu doko yanga paupau leya. Leyamopape baa soo gisa naya.
\v 30 Dopa piyamopa Eronemoo wambu dupwa pipya Mosesena lenge kambu doko yanga paupau lao lepo lepo piyamo doko kandapala nakama repeta panya pakayami.
\v 31 Dopa piyamopape Mosese nakama kee leya. Leyamo dokopa Eronemoo Isaraele wambunya akali mupwa dupwa pipya baa kareyamo dokona peyami. Peyaminyipa Moseseme nakama pii lamaiya.
\v 32 Enakana dokopa wambu peparae Mosese kareyamo dokona sukusa sukusa pyuo epeyami. Dopa piyaminyipa Kamongome yuu kyau Sainai dokona mawa pii maiyamo dupwa peparae wambu dupwa lamaiya.
\v 33 Mosese baame wambu dupwa pii lamaiyuo otapala dokopa komau mendeme banya lenge kambu doko yambe piya.
\v 34 Yuu lapo Mosese baa Kamongona komau anda dokona Kamongo pii lamaila papapu dokopa lenge kambunya komau yambe pingi doko neta nyingi. Dee baa kamanda epo dokopa Kamongome pii lamainya lao lamaingi dupwa peparae Isaraele wambu dupwa lamaipa pingi.
\v 35 Dokopa wambu dupwame banya lenge kambu doko yanga paupau lao lepo lepo pilyamo kandenge. Dokopa banya komau dokome lenge kambu yambe pingi doko pyaro karelyamopa pao yuu gii mendepa Kamongo pii lamaila panya dokopa nyisa nyingi.
\s3 35:1—40:16 Moseseme misi anda kapa pira lao Isaraele wambu dupwame Anatumi leyamuli pyuo Mosesemoo wambu dupwape bange malu mee minyuo epeyami. Dokopa komaumi misi anda pyuo oteyami.
\c 40
\s1 Mosese Baame Kamongona Komau // Anda Piya
\p 
\v 17 Nakama yuu Isipi yaki nyuo epapeyaminyi dokopa enakana ee kana lapona kana mupwa dokona yuu gii mupwa dokopa Kamongona komau anda doko kanda soo piyami.
\v 18 Moseseme isa yuu dokona susa pyao isa retapala wangu dupwa isa pyano piya. Dopa pipala wangu dokona isa lapo palyiya. Palyapala komau anda dokona kambu dowa dokona isa pote lapo pyaneya.
\v 19 Dopa pipala Kamongome pinya leyamuli pyuo baame komau anda doko komau mendeme wambo kaowapala dee enakana mendeme kamba lapo pyuo doko kao piya.
\v 20 Kaowapala baame kana para dolapo nyepala Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote dokona palyiya. Palyapala baame isa lama bokote pinjingi kingi minyingi dolapona pyambwapala bokote doko upi leya.
\v 21 Upi lapala baame bokote doko minyuo pao komau anda dokona retapala komau mendeme nee pyuo yukunyi palyiya. Dopa piyamo doko baame Kamongome leyamuli pyuo Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko yambe pyao reteya.
\p 
\v 22 Baame misi anda komaumi wasisi dokona taepo doko komau yukwaro kareyamo dokona kamarena kingi kyairena reteya.
\v 23 Kamongome leyamuli pyuo borete Kamongo kiso maingi dupwa taepo dokona ketae reteya.
\v 24 Baame misi anda komaumi wasisi dokona lambe kisingi bange doko minyuo pao taepo kanda kanda kingi rolaerename reteya.
\v 25 Retapala baame Kamongome leyamuli pyuo lambe dupwa Kamongona lenge kambu dokona kaiya.
\v 26 Baame kana golome wasisi kana pyare lasi minyuo pao komau anda kambu konando penge dokona komau yukwaro kareyamo lenge kambusa andakare reteya.
\v 27 Retapala Kamongome leyamuli pyuo rendamu kyaa keyange pingi bange dupwa dokona kisiya.
\v 28 Komau anda kambu konandowame dokona komau doko yukunyi palyiya.
\v 29 Doo komau yukuyamo dokona lenge kambusa kamarena mena pyao kiso maingi kana pyare lasi doko reteya. Reteyamo dokona baame Kamongome leyamuli pyuo mena pyao kiso maiyuo witi jingi dupwa kiso maiyuo piya.
\v 30 Pipala mena pyao kiso maingi kana pyare dokope komau andape kanya dokona wate pingi disi warake doko retapala dokona ipwa kamuo simbuo reteya.
\v 31-32 Kamongome lamaiyamuli pyuo Mosesemoo Eronemoo Erone banya ikinyingimoo yuu gii lapo nakama komau andape kana pyare lasi dokonape pena dokopa kingi kimbupi wate pipa pingi.
\v 33 Komau anda dokope bange kiso maingi kana pyare dokope laparae nyuo sukusa palyuo kame awali lao piya. Pipala kambu konando penge dokona komau doko yukunyi palyiya. Dopa pipala Moseseme yulu peparae pyuo oteya.
\s1 Kamongona Komau Anda Dokona Kopa Doko Epo Ketae Siya
\r (Nam 9:15-23)
\p 
\v 34 Misi anda komaumi wasisi dokona kopa dokome epo yambe piya. Dokopa Anatunya yanga paupau lenge renge dokome leya leya piyamo dokome komau anda doko palyuo simbuya.
\v 35 Dopa piyamosa Mosese komau anda dokona kolando paa naya.
\v 36 Kopa komau anda dokona siyamo doko sipuro peyamo dokopa iki Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu paleyaminyi doko yaki nyuo yuu mendasa parapu paleyami.
\v 37 Kopa doko mee dokona sulu siyamo dokopa nakama paleyaminyi yuu doko yaki nyuo paa nayami.
\v 38 Yuu gii peparae korakama dokopa nakama kata papyuo kareyaminyi dokopa kopa dokome Kamongo karamo lao lasaka pyuo komau anda ketae siyamo doko kandeyami. Dee kukwa dokopa komau anda ketae isare rao kareyamo kandeyami. 
